3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20risky%20%E2%80%94%20the%20NASA%20lasers%20were%20on%20the%20lander%20to%20test%20whether%20they%20worked%20in%20space%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20better%20than%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20controllers%20moved%20the%20spacecraft%20into%20a%20different%20orbit%20and%20pushed%20back%20the%20landing%20by%20about%2045%20minutes%2C%20buying%20them%20just%20enough%20time%20to%20upload%20a%20software%20patch%20that%20gave%20the%20lander%20its%20new%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20normal%20software%20development%20for%20a%20spacecraft%2C%20this%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20that%20would%20have%20taken%20a%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Crain%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20team%20basically%20did%20that%20in%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half.%20And%20it%20worked.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20finest%20pieces%20of%20engineering%20I've%20ever%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20be%20affiliated%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintuitive-machines-ceo-safety-switch-almost-lost-odysseus-moon-landing-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708741021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d94bd290413ab8e1d6a151%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintuitive-machines-ceo-safety-switch-almost-lost-odysseus-moon-landing-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Intuitive%20Machines%20almost%20lost%20its%20moon%20landing%20after%20someone%20forgot%20to%20flip%20a%20switch%20before%20launch.%20The%20Odysseus%20lander%20is%20now%20sideways%20on%20the%20moon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmcfalljohnsen%40businessinsider.com%20(Morgan%20McFall-Johnsen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintuitive-machines-ceo-safety-switch-almost-lost-odysseus-moon-landing-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%2