ehind%20bars%20through%20CBI.%20Until%20BJP%20felt%20that%20an%20alliance%20between%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20would%20not%20be%20possible%2C%20they%20went%20into%20waiting%20mode.%20As%20the%20alliance%20took%20a%20concrete%20shape%2C%20the%20BJP%20started%20attacking%20AAP.%20Even%20if%20they%20(BJP)%20are%20using%20ED%20and%20CBI%20as%20their%20political%20frontal%20organisations%2C%20AAP%20will%20not%20be%20afraid%20of%20them.%20We%20will%20democratically%20face%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20is%20so%20scared%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20that%20now%20CBI%20pressure%20is%20being%20put%20on%20us%20so%20that%20we%20come%20out%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Shehzad%20Poonawalla%20said%20that%20the%20guarantee%20of%20Chinese%20products%20are%20more%20than%20the%20statements%20given%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20allegations%20made%20by%20AAP%20are%20less%20credible%20than%20the%20things%20we%20get%20in%20the%20'chor%20bazaar'.%20The%20guarantee%20of%20Chinese%20products%20is%20more%20than%20the%20statement%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20This%20is%20because%20whenever%20they%20made%20allegations%20be%20it%20on%20Arun%20Jaitley%20or%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20they%20had%20to%20apologise.%20First%20they%20alleged%20that%20BJP%20wants%20to%20break%20their%20MLAs%2C%20till%20date%20no%20proof%20of%20this%20has%20come.%20When%20the%20police%20reached%20them%2C%20they%20ran%20away%20from%20there.%20They%20have%20left%20Anna%20Hazare%20and%20have%20joined%20Lalu%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20whom%20they%20cursed%20for%20corruption.%20He%20(Arvind%20Kejriwal)%20knows%20that%20he%20won't%20get%20any%20relaxation%20in%20the%20liquor%20scam%20and%20thus%20he%20is%20playing%20victimhood%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Delhi%20Minister%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20on%20Friday%20claimed%20that%20Delhi%20Chief%2