0described%20emotional%20challenges%2C%20including%20reporting%20on%20civilian%20and%20soldier%20deaths.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EReporters%20highlighted%20the%20crucial%20roles%20of%20their%20colleagues%20on%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWar%20correspondents%20covering%20Russia's%20brutal%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20for%20the%20news%20outlet%20Current%20Time%20described%20the%20horrific%20scenes%20they%20witnessed%20and%20how%20they%20grapple%20with%20them%20as%20they%20continue%20to%20cover%20the%20war%20going%20into%20its%20third%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20been%20horrific%2C%20claiming%20countless%20lives%2C%20both%20military%20and%20civilian%2C%20and%20there%20have%20been%20numerous%20atrocities%20and%20war%20crimes%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20been%20carefully%20documented%20by%20reporters%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%20are%20the%20bodies%20of%2015%20civilians%20killed%20by%20Russian%20soldiers%2C%26quot%3B%20Andriy%20Kuzakov%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rferl.org%2Fa%2Ftwo-years-war-current-time-correspondents-ukraine-front-line%2F32832444.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Radio%20Free%20Europe%2C%20detailing%20a%20darker%20war%20story.%20%26quot%3BThey%20piled%20them%20up%2C%20poured%20gasoline%20over%20them%2C%20and%20burned%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuzakov%20explained%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20often%20witnessing%20other%20people's%20grief%2C%20he%20has%20also%20experienced%20the%20tragic%20nature%20of%20the%20war%20while%20working%20to%20cover%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20normal%20scene%20for%20us%20when%20a%20mother%20turned%20over%20her%20son's%20body%2C%20talking%20to%20him%20as%20if%20he%20was%20a%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20correspondent%2C%20Borys%20Sachalko%2C%20said%2C%20describing%20the%20discovery%20of%20a%20mass%20grave%20and%20interactions%20with%20the%20people%20in%20the%20Ukrainian%20settlement%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-russia-killings-borodyanka-likely-worse-bucha-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBorodyanka%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%2040-year-old%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20journalist%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20she%20was%20still%20his%20mother.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorodyanka%20is%20located%20near%20Kyiv%20and%20like%20Bucha%20was%20the%20site%20of%20many%20reported%20atrocities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20spoke%20about%20this%20in%20April%202022%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20many%20villages%20of%20the%20liberated%20districts%20of%20the%20Kyiv%2C%20Chernihiv%20and%20Sumy%20regions%2C%20the%20occupiers%20did%20things%20that%20the%20locals%20had%20not%20seen%20even%20during%20the%20Nazi%20occupation%2080%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESachalko%20said%20that%20while%20these%20scenes%20are%20deeply%20tragic%2C%20he%20feels%20he%20must%20%26quot%3Bcut%20off%26quot%3B%20his%20emotions.%20That's%20not%20always%20possible%20though.%20He%20said%20that%20sometimes%20after%20replaying%20footage%2C%20he%20gives%20into%20his%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorrespondent%20Oleksiy%20Prodayvoda%20said%20the%20most%20difficult%20aspect%20of%20his%20work%20is%20getting%20to%20know%20soldiers%20and%20then%20later%20hearing%20that%20they've%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProdayvoda%20added%20that%20there%20have%20been%20times%20where%20he%20has%20been%20notified%20that%20a%20soldier%20fell%20before%20he%20had%20finished%20reporting%20a%20story%20on%20them.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20the%20ending%20you%20want%20to%20add%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fwhy-support-from-the-global-south-is-critical-for-peace-in-ukraine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20the%20journalists%20have%20counted%20on%20their%20colleagues%2C%20such%20as%20their%20drivers%2C%20to%20help%20keep%20them%20safe%20and%20keep%20up%20morale.%20It's%20a%20tough%20and%20challenging%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20focused%20on%20press%20global%20freedom%2C%20reports%20that%20between%202022%20and%202024%2C%20over%20a%20dozen%20civilian%20journalists%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20course%20of%20covering%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20a%20number%20of%20others%20have%20been%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjournalists-share-horror-stories-from-ukraine-war-how-they-cope-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708721326000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8eaa06080194819f9d2dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjournalists-share-horror-stories-from-ukraine-war-how-they-cope-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Journalists%20have%20shared%20the%20harsh%20realities%20of%20reporting%20on%20the%20Ukrainian%20war%20and%20its%20atrocities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ella%20Sherman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjournalists-share-horror-stories-from-ukraine-war-how-they-cope-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20investors%20can%20avoid%20a%20lost%20decade%20for%20stocks%20whenever%20the%20tech%20bubble%20pops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Watsonx%20AI%20IBM%20generative%20AI%20platform%20displayed%20on%20a%20smartphone%20with%20Meta%20AI.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8d73090413ab8e1d67658%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPhoto%20illustration%20by%20Jonathan%20Raa%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20giants%20keep%20gaining%2C%20concerns%20of%20stock-market%20concentration%20are%20rising.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20bursting%20of%20the%20AI%20bubble%20could%20see%20a%20lost%20decade%20for%20stocks%20similar%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20dot-com%20boom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDiversifying%20portfolios%20is%20key%20for%20investors%20to%20avoid%20losses%20if%20the%20bubble%20deflates%2C%20Richard%20Bernstein%20told%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20artificial%20intelligence%20craze%20marches%20on%2C%20and%20with%20it%2C%20fears%20of%20growing%20concentration%20in%20the%20stock%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E's%20smash-hit%20earnings%20for%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20added%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-price-added-entire-netflix-market-cap-value-nvda-2024-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNvidia%2527s%2520current%2520market%2520valuation%2520is%2520%25241.95%2520trillion.%5C%22%3E%24267%20billion%20to%20its%20market%20cap%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%2C%20more%20than%20Netflix's%20entire%20value%20and%20setting%20a%20record%20for%20the%20largest%20single-day%20gain%20in%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20wrap%20up%20their%20latest%20earnings%20season%2C%20it's%20fair%20to%20say%20that%20the%20AI%20trade%20is%20in%20full%20swing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20with%20such%20narrow%20leadership%2C%20analysts%20have%20warned%20of%20an%20AI-driven%20tech%20bubble%20reminiscent%20of%20two%20decades%20ago.%20Similar%20to%20that%20period%2C%20warnings%20are%20growing%20that%20the%20latest%20bubble%20will%20also%20burst.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20important%20thing%20to%20remember%20is%20that%20bubbles%20ALWAYS%20center%20around%20a%20new%20technology%20or%20a%20new%20development.%C2%A0%20It's%20a%20bit%20different%20in%20that%20so%20far%E2%80%A6so%20far%E2%80%A6it%20hasn't%20resulted%20in%20widespread%20new%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Richard%20Bernstein%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Richard%20Bernstein%20Advisors%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20popping%20of%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20ushered%20in%20a%20lost%20decade%20for%20the%20stock%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%201999%20to%202009%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20returned%20-1%25%20per%20year%2C%20and%20the%20Nasdaq%20fared%20even%20worse%20at%20-5%25%20per%20year%20(-6%25%20per%20year%20for%20the%20Nasdaq%20100).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20if%20one%20had%20bought%20NASDAQ%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20Tech%20Bubble%20in%20March%202000%2C%20it%20would've%20taken%20nearly%2014%20years%20to%20simply%20break%20even%2C%26quot%3B%20Richard%20Bernstein%20Advisors%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20last%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20there's%20a%20simple%20solution%20to%20avoiding%20the%20dot-com%20era%20fate%20that%20befell%20investors%2C%20RBA%20says%3A%20diversify.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShunning%20diversification%20has%20never%20been%20prudent%2C%20and%20that's%20certainly%20true%20during%20bubble%20environments.%20The%20key%20to%20future%20returns%20may%20be%20simple%2C%20basic%20diversification.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EThe%20Top%20Six%20vs.%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20final%20year%20of%20the%20tech%20bubble%20in%201999%2C%20the%20thrill%20of%20internet%20technology%20and%20its%20potential%20to%20revolutionize%20the%20economy%20quickly%20inflated%20a%20handful%20of%20stocks%2C%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20Information%20Technology%20sector%20generating%20a%20total%20return%20of%20103.76%25%20that%20year%2C%20RBA%20noted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%26quot%3Bold%20economy%26quot%3B%20stocks%20were%20left%20behind%20by%20tech%2C%20with%20the%20six%20other%20major%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20sectors%20generating%20an%20average%20return%20of%2010.7%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERBA%20analysis%20said%20many%20investors%20believe%20that%20today's%20%26quot%3BAI%20bubble%26quot%3B%20is%20wildly%20different%20from%20bubbles%20of%20years'%20past%20because%20the%20mega-cap%20leaders%20are%20%26quot%3Breal%20companies%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20those%20that%20commanded%20lofty%20valuations%20with%20little%20earnings%20to%20back%20them%20up.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20misconception%2C%20Bernstein%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20largest%20tech%20titans%20as%20of%20December%201999%20%E2%80%93%20Microsoft%2C%20Cisco%2C%20Intel%2C%20IBM%2C%20Oracle%2C%20and%20Qualcomm%20%E2%80%94%20were%20legitimate%20companies%20with%20robust%20financial%20positions%20and%20positive%20cash%20flow%20at%20the%20time.%20But%20when%20the%20bubble%20deflated%2C%20none%20of%20those%20stocks%20saw%20a%20speedy%20recovery%20to%20previous%20highs.%20Cisco%20stock%20wouldn't%20recover%20fully%20until%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20AI-fueled%20bubble%20and%20pandemic-related%20excess%20liquidity%20have%20pumped%20up%20stock%20valuations%2C%20leading%20to%20highly%20speculative%20and%20concentrated%20market%20leadership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Magnificent%20Seven%20stocks%20%E2%80%94%20Alphabet%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Apple%2C%20Meta%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20Tesla%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftech-stocks-magnificent-7-dot-com-1999-bubble-inflation-recession-2024-2%3F_gl%3D1*1ruiqt*_ga*MTIzMDA5Njk4OS4xNzA3ODc2NDgz*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTcwODcwNjQxMy4zMy4xLjE3MDg3MDgyOTkuNTQuMC4w%5C%22%3Eaccount%20for%20roughly%2029%25%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20these%20days%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bernstein%20said%20despite%20some%20of%20those%20names%20showing%20solid%20fundamental%20growth%2C%20the%20growth%20isn't%20exceptional%20compared%20to%20many%20other%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20currently%20about%20140%20stocks%20within%20the%20G-7%20equity%20markets%20(US%2C%20Canada%2C%20Germany%2C%20Japan%2C%20France%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20Italy)%20projected%20to%20grow%20earnings%2025%25%20or%20more%20over%20the%20next%20year.%C2%A0%20Most%20importantly%2C%20only%203%20of%20the%20Magnificent%207%20pass%20the%20screen%20and%20the%20fastest%20growing%20of%20the%20Magnificent%207%20ranks%20only%2025th%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20note.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiversification%20is%20key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein%20reiterated%20that%20investors%20have%20to%20diversify%20their%20portfolios%20to%20avoid%20future%20losses%20that%20dragged%20down%20portfolios%20in%20the%20years%20after%20the%20dot-com%20bust.%20Luckily%2C%20the%20range%20of%20sound%20investments%20outside%20of%20the%20largest%20stocks%20amounts%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bonce%20in%20a%20generation%26quot%3B%20opportunity%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-buy-signal-sp500-tech-stock-bubble-rba-2024-1%5C%22%3ERBA%20has%20argued.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20view%20of%20the%20world%20proves%20incorrect%2C%20then%20you'll%20have%20something%20that's%20likely%20to%20outperform%20in%20that%20unanticipated%20scenario.%20So%2C%20there%20should%20always%20be%20a%20spare%20tire%20in%20the%20portfolio%20in%20case%20you're%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20made%20a%20distinction%20between%20%26quot%3Beconomy%20opportunities%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binvestment%20opportunities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnology%20always%20changes%20the%20economy.%20My%20favorite%20'technology'%20that%20significantly%20changed%20the%20economy%20was%20the%20light%20bulb%20because%20it%20turned%20the%20economy%20into%20a%2024-hour%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAI%20will%20change%20the%20economy%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20investing%20in%20the%20accepted%20AI%20stock%20today%20will%20prove%20profitable%20over%20the%20longer-term.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-stocks-ai-bubble-dot-com-lost-decade-rba-nvda-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708721087000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d8d750ce7f1785b2e382fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftech-stocks-ai-bubble-dot-com-lost-decade-rba-nvda-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Buying%20the%20Nasdaq%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20dot-com%20boom%20in%20March%202000%20meant%20waiting%20nearly%2014%20years%20to%20break%20even%2C%20according%20to%20Richard%20Bernstein.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22yzhan%40insider.com%20(Yuheng%20Zhan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftech-stocks-ai-bubble-dot-com-lost-decade-rba-nvda-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Palestinian-Algerian%20Rapper%20Saint%20Levant%20Drops%20%E2%80%98Deira%E2%80%99%20Single%20With%20MC%20Abdul%2C%20Paying%20Tribute%20to%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708720870000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthumbnail_E75F268E-3376-47CF-A3C5-7BFA1652F4DE.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235920925%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Palestinian%20musicians%20Saint%20Levant%20and%20MC%20Abdul%20have%20united%20to%20release%20%E2%80%9CDeira%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20sees%20the%20two%20artists%20paying%20peaceful%20tribute%20to%20the%20people%20and%20culture%20of%20Gaza%20and%20performing%20in%20traditional%20Shaabi%20Ar