blow%20dryer%20brush%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20just%20because%20it's%20incredibly%20expensive%20at%20nearly%20%24550.%20The%20Airwrap%20utilizes%20innovative%20technology%20to%20pull%20hair%20towards%20the%20device.%20The%20built-in%20thermistor%20helps%20regulate%20temperature%20and%20prevent%20your%20strands%20from%20burning.%20It%20also%20comes%20with%20six%20attachments%2C%20including%20a%20round%20brush%2C%20flat%20brush%2C%20and%20several%20curling%20barrels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20under%20%2450%3A%20Trademark%20Beauty%20Babe%20Waves%20Easy%20Blo%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20styling%20their%20hair%20using%20the%20Trademark%20Beauty%20Babe%20Waves%20Easy%20Blo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f818da45edd800183b5bb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20ultra-lightweight%20blow%20dryer%20brush%20comes%20complete%20with%20combination%20bristles%2C%20a%20cool%20setting%2C%20and%20powerful%20airflow.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDespite%20how%20lightweight%20it%20is%2C%20the%20barrel%20is%20large%20%E2%80%94%20and%20perhaps%20may%20be%20too%20large%20for%20those%20with%20shorter%20hair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDitch%20your%20basic%2C%20bulky%20hairdryer%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20Trademark%20Beauty%20Easy%20Blo.%20Weighing%20just%20under%20one%20pound%2C%20this%20blow%20dryer%20brush%20is%20among%20the%20lightest%20on%20the%20market.%20And%2C%20according%20to%20Amy%20Abramite%2C%20Creative%20Director%20and%20Stylist%20at%20Maxine%20Salon%20in%20Chicago%2C%20the%20tool%20%26quot%3Bchecks%20all%20the%20boxes%20for%20a%20great%20beauty%20buy.%26quot%3B%20The%20cool%20setting%20is%20a%20bonus%2C%20as%20are%20the%20combination%20bristles%20(nylon%20to%20detangle%20and%20boar%20to%20smooth%20and%20tame%20frizz).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20tried%20other%20dryers%2C%20and%20this%20model%20stands%20out%20for%20its%20lightweight%20design%20and%20powerful%20airflow%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20stylist%20tells%20Insider.%20Additionally%2C%20according%20to%20Abramite%2C%20this%20tool%20offers%20users%20the%20chance%20to%20%26quot%3Bquickly%20get%20a%20salon-quality%20blowout%20without%20fatigue%20from%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20tool%2C%20which%20typically%20accompanies%20high%20wattage%20dryers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20blow%20dryer%20brush%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20blow%20dryer%20brushes%20on%20the%20market%2C%20keep%20in%20mind%20all%20of%20the%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShape%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shape%20of%20the%20blow%20dryer%20brush%20directly%20impacts%20the%20type%20of%20result%20you'll%20get.%20For%20example%2C%20paddle%20dryer%20brushes%2C%20such%20as%20Dyson's%20flat%20attachment%2C%20are%20great%20for%20producing%20straight%2C%20sleek%20blowouts.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20round%20or%20oval-shaped%20brushes%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Revlon%20One%20Step%20and%20Drybar%20Double%20Shot%2C%20are%20ideal%20for%20bouncier%2C%20more%20voluminous%20blowouts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20finding%20the%20best%20blow%20dryer%20brush%20to%20suit%20your%20individual%20needs%2C%20size%20definitely%20does%20matter.%20Put%20simply%2C%20the%20smaller%20the%20barrel%2C%20the%20tighter%20the%20curl.%20Wider%20barrels%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20create%20loose%20waves%20and%20flips%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes.%20In%20terms%20of%20range%2C%20the%20smallest%20barrels%20over%20around%201.25%20to%201.5%20inches%20while%20the%20largest%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20Bedhead%20One%20Step%20Volumizer%20%E2%80%94%20clock%20in%20at%204.5%20inches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIonic%20technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20dozens%20of%20great%20options%20on%20the%20market%2C%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20best%20blow%20dryer%20brushes%20feature%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-hair-dryer%5C%22%3Eionic%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20help%20minimize%20frizz%20and%20enhance%20shine.%20The%20result%3F%20Frizz-free%2C%20softer%20strands%20in%20mere%20minutes.%20Also%2C%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20shell%20out%20half%20a%20week's%20paycheck%20on%20a%20blow-dryer%20brush%3A%20There%20are%20plenty%20of%20great%20affordable%20options%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-dyson-airwrap-dupes%5C%22%3Edupes%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%20there%2C%20too!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBristle%20material%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20shop%20for%20the%20best%20blow%20dryer%20brush%2C%20consider%20the%20bristle%20material.%20It's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20some%20of%20the%20best%20blow%20dryer%20brushes%20contain%20a%20combination%20of%20different%20bristles.%C2%A0%20Nylon%20bristles%20are%20firm%20yet%20gentle%20(which%20means%20they%20won't%20cause%20tugging%20or%20tanging)%2C%20while%20silicone%20bristles%20are%20more%20flexible.%20Boar%20bristles%20are%20made%20of%20%E2%80%94%20you%20guessed%20it%20%E2%80%94%20the%20hair%20of%20boars.%20These%20natural%20bristles%20easily%20glide%20through%20the%20hair%20while%20gently%20massaging%20the%20scalp.%20This%20can%20help%20minimize%20frizz%2C%20too.%20While%20different%20bristle%20types%20have%20different%20benefits%2C%20Toth%20recommends%20looking%20for%20a%20blow%20dryer%20brush%20that%20contains%20both%20boar%20and%20nylon%20bristles%2C%20which%20can%20be%20found%20in%20picks%20like%20the%20Conair%20Hot%20Air%20Spin%20Brush.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVoltage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20frequent%20flier%20and%20a