%20the%20jet%20stream%2C%20Bangs%20said.%20That's%20when%20turbulence%20can%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20make%20a%20pilot's%20job%20harder%2C%20but%20as%20for%20the%20plane%20itself%2C%20they%20%26quot%3Bare%20engineered%20to%20take%20or%20absorb%20turbulence%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20turbulent%20flights%2C%20passengers%20might%20notice%20the%20plane's%20wings%20bending%20and%20flexing%2C%20and%20that's%20on%20purpose%2C%20Bangs%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20disconcerting%20to%20passengers%2C%20but%20it's%20how%20airliners%20are%20designed%2C%20and%20it%20increases%20their%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20former%20pilot%20said%20cruising%20in%20fast%20winds%20is%20'fun'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChances%20are%2C%20your%20pilot%20isn't%20just%20ending%20up%20in%20a%20jet%20stream%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20looking%20for%20one%2C%20LaFauci%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirline%20dispatchers%20will%20help%20plan%20routes%20in%20jet%20streams%20because%20%26quot%3Bthis%20leads%20to%20shorter%20route%20times%2C%20less%20fuel%20consumed%2C%20better%20efficiency%2C%20etc.%2C'%26quot%3B%20LaFauci%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20happy%20passengers%2C%20Bangs%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20fun%20in%20the%20cockpit%20is%20to%20watch%20your%20ground%20speed%20on%20the%20avionics%20computer%20screen%20increase%20and%20increase%20until%20you're%20sailing%20through%20the%20air%20over%20700-750%20mph%20ground%20speed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20some%20aviators%20recently%20%E2%80%94%20over%20800%20mph%2C%26quot%3B%20Bangs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBangs%20said%20pilots%20are%20trained%20for%20turbulence%20and%20briefed%20ahead%20of%20time%20on%20the%20weather.%20This%20gives%20them%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20what%20to%20expect%20on%20the%20flight%20and%20allows%20them%20to%20communicate%20with%20passengers%20about%20a%20potentially%20bumpy%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Bangs%20said%2C%20%26q