D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhich%20Law%20Gives%20Legitimacy%20To%20Child%20Born%20Outside%20Formal%20Marriage%3F%26quot%3B%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20sought%20to%20know%20which%20law%20gives%20legitimacy%20to%20children%20born%20outside%20a%20formal%20marriage%2C%20be%20it%20void%20or%20voidable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20voidable%20marriage%20is%20one%20that%20can%20be%20rendered%20invalid%20by%20the%20husband%20or%20wife%20through%20a%20decree%2C%20while%20a%20void%20marriage%20is%20invalid%20at%20the%20very%20inception.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%20sought%20to%20know%20the%20existing%20law%20which%20gives%20legitimacy%20to%20children%20born%20outside%20marriage%20while%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20pleas%20challenging%20various%20provisions%20and%20rules%20of%20Surrogacy%20(regulations)%20Rules%2C%202022%20and%20Assisted%20Reproductive%20Technology%20(Regulations)%20(ART)%20Act%20of%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20disposed%20of%20a%20number%20of%20petitions%20in%20view%20of%20the%20Centre's%20February%2021%20notification%20amending%20the%20Surrogacy%20Rules%202022%20and%20allowing%20married%20couples%20to%20use%20an%20egg%20or%20sperm%20of%20a%20donor%20in%20case%20one%20of%20the%20partners%20is%20suffering%20from%20a%20medical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhich%20is%20the%20law%20that%20gives%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20children%20born%20outside%20a%20formal%20marriage%2C%20let%20it%20be%20void%20or%20voidable.%20There%20must%20be%20a%20ceremony%20of%20marriage.%20It%20may%20be%20a%20void%20marriage%20or%20it%20may%20be%20a%20voidable%20marriage.%20Outside%20the%20ceremony%20of%20marriage%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20formal%20ceremony.%20Please%20enlighten%20us%2C%20which%20is%20the%20law%20which%20gives%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagarathna%20asked%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20the%20counsel%20representing%20the%20petitioners%20challenging%20various%20provisions%20of%20surrogacy%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20for%20availing%20the%20benefit%20of%20surrogacy%20provisions%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20an%20attempt%20for%20conception%20within%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20having%20an%20open%20mind%20but%20we%20are%20indicating%20what%20it%20is.%20What%20is%20the%20basis%20of%20our%20indication%2C%20we%20are%20saying%20that.%20Conception%20within%20marriage%20is%20what%20you%20call%20a%20legitimate%20child.%20Even%20in%20the%20case%20of%20section%2016%20of%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20marriage.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20a%20void%20marriage%2C%20then%20only%20the%20illegitimate%20children%20will%20get%20the%20legitimacy%20under%20section%2016%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act.%20Is%20there%20any%20other%20law%20which%20gives%20them%20legitimacy%2C%20please%20tell%20us.%20Enlighten%20us%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2016%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%20states%20that%20notwithstanding%20that%20marriage%20is%20null%20and%20void%20under%20the%20law%2C%20any%20child%20of%20such%20marriage%20who%20would%20have%20been%20legitimate%20if%20the%20marriage%20had%20been%20valid%2C%20shall%20be%20legitimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Act%2C%20a%20marriage%20can%20be%20declared%20as%20void%20if%20either%20party%20is%20already%20married%2C%20if%20the%20parties%20are%20related%20to%20each%20other%20within%20the%20degrees%20of%20sapinda%20relationship%2C%20or%20if%20either%20party%20is%20below%20the%20legal%20age%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bhati%20said%20the%20Centre%20will%20assist%20the%20court%20on%20the%20issue%20but%20submissions%20with%20regard%20to%20legitimate%20or%20illegitimate%20children%20have%20not%20been%20made%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court's%20judgement%20is%20there%20on%20legitimate%20or%20illegitimate%20children.%20There%20are%20no%20illegitimate%20children%20anymore.%20That%20whole%20concept%20is%20gone.%20But%20we%20will%20assist%20this%20court%20in%20taking%20a%20view%20on%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bhati%20said%20at%20present%20there%20are%20four%20ways%20in%20which%20children%20can%20be%20had%20--%20one%20can%20be%20a%20natural%20birth%2C%20through%20ART%2C%20where%20a%20woman%20can%20be%20assisted%20to%20have%20a%20child%20herself%2C%20then%20it%20is%20adoption%2C%20where%20you%20don't%20give%20birth%20to%20the%20child%20and%20the%20last%20is%20surrogacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20it%20is%20not%20disposing%20of%20the%20petitions%20of%20single%20unmarried%20women%20seeking%20benefit%20of%20the%20surrogacy%20law%20and%20those%20that%20have%20challenged%20other%20provisions%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20asked%20Ms%20Bhati%20to%20file%20written%20submissions%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20single%20unmarried%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%20said%20medical%20reports%20of%20some%20of%20the%20petitioners%20as%20required%20under%20the%20surrogacy%20law%20are%20yet%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20see%20the%20reports%20of%20the%20medical%20board%20and%20then%20proceed.%20Unless%20they%20come%20under%20Rule%2014%2C%20we%20cannot%20allow%20them%20to%20proceed%20for%20surrogacy.%20You%20see%20Rule%2014%20is%20the%20basis%20for%20surrogacy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERule%2014%20gives%20details%20of%20medical%20conditions%20where%20a%20woman%20may%20opt%20for%20surrogacy%20like%20if%20she%20has%20no%20uterus%20or%20abnormal%20uterus%20or%20if%20the%20uterus%20is%20surgically%20removed%20due%20to%20any%20medical%20conditions%20such%20as%20gynaecological%20cancers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20appreciated%20the%20Centre%20for%20taking%20the%20issue%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20spirit%26quot%3B%20and%20issuing%20a%20notification%20amending%20the%20surrogacy%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20February%2021%20notification%2C%20the%20Centre%20amended%20the%20surrogacy%20rules%20of%202022%20allowing%20married%20couples%20to%20use%20an%20egg%20or%20sperm%20of%20a%20donor%20in%20case%20one%20of%20the%20partners%20is%20suffering%20from%20a%20medical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20in%20March%202023%20issued%20a%20notification%20banning%20donor%20gametes%20for%20couples%20intending%20to%20undergo%20surrogacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708714320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhich-law-gives-legitimacy-to-child-born-outside-formal-marriage-supreme-court-5115482%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20sought%20to%20know%20which%20law%20gives%20legitimacy%20to%20children%20born%20outside%20a%20formal%20marriage%2C%20be%20it%20void%20or%20voidable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhich-law-gives-legitimacy-to-child-born-outside-formal-marriage-supreme-court-5115482%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhich-law-gives-legitimacy-to-child-born-outside-formal-marriage-supreme-court-5115482%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhich-law-gives-legitimacy-to-child-born-outside-formal-marriage-supreme-court-5115482%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Citizenship%20not%20an%20issue%3A%20HC%2C%20gives%20kid's%20custody%20to%20Banglad