2%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbhagyashree-celebrates-her-55th-birthday-with-family-madhuri-dixit-madhoo-anupam-kher-among-other-celebs-attend-the-bash%2Farticleshow%2F107952062.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Setback%20For%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20Karnataka%20Bill%20To%20Tax%20Temples%20Defeated%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20setback%20for%20the%20Congress-led%20government%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20a%20bill%20that%20mandated%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20the%20income%20of%20temples%20that%20have%20revenues%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20crore%20was%20defeated%20in%20the%20state%20legislative%20council%20late%20this%20evening.%20This%20comes%20two%20days%20after%20the%20bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20sparked%20a%20huge%20controversy%20in%20Karnataka%20with%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20accusing%20the%20Congress%20of%20implementing%20'Anti-Hindu'%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20has%20more%20numbers%20than%20the%20ruling%20government%20in%20the%20legislative%20council%20or%20Upper%20House%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20Congress%20has%2030%20MLCs%2C%20BJP%20has%2035%2C%20eight%20MLCs%20are%20from%20the%20JD(S)%20and%20there%20is%20one%20independent%20candidate.%20One%20seat%20is%20vacant%20in%20the%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20government%20passed%20'Karnataka%20Hindu%20Religious%20Institutions%20and%20Charitable%20Endowment%20Amendment%20Bill%202024'%20that%20mandates%20the%20state%20to%20collect%2010%20per%20cent%20tax%20from%20temples%20that%20have%20revenues%20exceeding%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%205%20pe%20rcent%20from%20those%20with%20revenues%20ranging%20between%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20flak%20regarding%20the%20government's%20amendments%20to%20the%20bill%2C%20state%20ministers%20Ramalinga%20Reddy%20and%20Dinesh%20Gundu%20Rao%20defended%20the%20move%20and%20criticised%20the%20BJP%20for%20its%20opposition%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinister%20for%20Transport%2C%20Ramalinga%20Reddy%20alleging%20that%20BJP%20is%20%26quot%3Banti-Hindu%26quot%3B%20claimed%20that%20the%20party%20which%20was%20in%20power%20in%202011%20had%20made%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20anti-Hindu.%20Actually%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20anti-Hindu.%20This%20Act%20came%20into%20existence%20in%202003.%20In%202011%2C%20they%20made%20some%20amendments.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%2C%20there%20were%20about%2034%2C000%20temples%20-%20they%20did%20not%20give%20any%20money%20for%20Dharmika%20Parishad.%20From%20Rs%205%20Lakhs%20to%20Rs%2010%20Lakhs%2C%20there%20are%20about%20193%20'B%20grade'%20temples%20-%20they%20have%20to%20give%205%20per%20cent.%20More%20than%20Rs%2010%20Lakhs%2C%20there%20are%20about%20205%20temples%20-%20they%20have%20to%20give%2010%20per%20cent.%20They%20approved%20this%20amendment%20in%202011%20in%20the%20Assembly.%20Who%20is%20anti-Hindu%3F%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinister%20for%20Health%20Dinesh%20Gundu%20Rao%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20should%20realise%20the%20bill%20is%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20temples%2C%20alleging%20that%20when%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20help%20smaller%20temples%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20mislead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20bill%20was%20cleared%20in%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20the%20state%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20veteran%20BS%20Yediyurappa%20questioned%20why%20only%20Hindu%20temples%20are%20being%20scrutinized%20and%20not%20the%20incomes%20of%20other%20religions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20that%20the%20allegations%20regarding%20the%20amendments%20to%20the%20bill%20%26quot%3Bappear%20to%20be%20misrepresented%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Baiming%20only%20at%20misleading%20the%20public%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpolarizing%20people%20along%20communal%20lines%20for%20political%20leverage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708712820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F1stgbbq_siddaramaiah_625x300_29_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsetback-for-siddaramaiah-karnataka-bill-to-tax-temples-defeated-in-legislative-council-5115258%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Setback%20for%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20Karnataka%20Bill%20to%20tax%20temples%20defeated%20in%20legislative%20council%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsetback-for-siddaramaiah-karnataka-bill-to-tax-temples-defeated-in-legislative-council-5115258%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsetback-for-siddaramaiah-karnataka-bill-to-tax-temples-defeated-in-legislative-council-5115258%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsetback-for-siddaramaiah-karnataka-bill-to-tax-temples-defeated-in-legislative-council-5115258%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%20To%20Repeal%20Muslim%20Marriage%20Act%20In%20Big%20Push%20For%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20three%20weeks%20after%20Uttarakhand%20became%20the%20first%20state%20in%20independent%20India%20to%20pass%20legislation%20on%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20Assam%20has%20taken%20its%20first%20step%20towards%20a%20similar%20law%20and%20decided%20to%20repeal%20the%20Muslim%20Marriage%20and%20Divorce%20Registration%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20the%20announcement%20on%20Friday%2C%20Assam%20Minister%20Jayanta%20Malla%20Baruah%20said%20the%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20by%20the%20cabinet.%20Sources%20said%20a%20bill%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20tabled%20in%20the