0bills%2C%20so%20we%20will%20have%20a%20round%20of%20discussion%20with%20our%20central%20leaders%20as%20well.%20These%20are%20long-time%20reforms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708712760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fu743q1go_himanta-biswa-sarma_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-cabinet-repeals-muslim-marriage-and-divorce-act-in-first-step-towards-uniform-civil-code-5115187%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Less%20than%20three%20weeks%20after%20Uttarakhand%20became%20the%20first%20state%20in%20independent%20India%20to%20pass%20legislation%20on%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20Assam%20has%20taken%20its%20first%20step%20towards%20a%20similar%20law%20by%20repealing%20the%20Muslim%20Marriage%20and%20Divorce%20Act.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-cabinet-repeals-muslim-marriage-and-divorce-act-in-first-step-towards-uniform-civil-code-5115187%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-cabinet-repeals-muslim-marriage-and-divorce-act-in-first-step-towards-uniform-civil-code-5115187%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-cabinet-repeals-muslim-marriage-and-divorce-act-in-first-step-towards-uniform-civil-code-5115187%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Then%20and%20now%3A%20Protesting%20farmers%20want%20their%20voice%20to%20reach%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708712619000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F23%2Ffull%2F1708712432-9592.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fthen-and-now-protesting-farmers-want-their-voice-to-reach-delhi-124022301282_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Similar%20langar%20set-