in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20TMC%20chairperson%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20stated%20that%20Trinamool%20Congress%20is%20fighting%20all%20the%2042%20seats%20in%20Bengal.%20We%20are%20also%20in%20the%20fray%20in%20a%20few%20seats%20in%20Assam%20and%20the%20Tura%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Meghalaya.%20There%20is%20no%20change%20in%20this%20position.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strong%20statement%20will%20come%20as%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20finalised%20a%20seat-sharing%20deal%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20has%20also%20reportedly%20worked%20out%20an%20understanding%20with%20the%20AAP%20for%20Delhi%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Goa%20and%20Haryana%20in%20the%20past%20few%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pact%20in%20West%20Bengal%20would%20not%20only%20have%20been%20a%20major%20morale%20boost%20for%20the%20opposition%20bloc%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20some%20major%20exits%20of%20late%2C%20but%20would%20have%20also%20been%20important%20electorally%20because%20the%20state%20sends%20the%20third-highest%20number%20of%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indications%20on%20Thursday%20were%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20scaled%20down%20its%20demand%20for%20seats%20in%20West%20Bengal%20to%20five%20and%20was%20looking%20to%20score%20a%20hat-trick%20with%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20after%20its%20successes%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20AAP.%20To%20sweeten%20a%20potential%20deal%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20reportedly%20willing%20to%20offer%20two%20seats%20to%20the%20Trinamool%20in%20Assam%20and%20one%20in%20Meghalaya.%20Congress%20sources%20had%20said%20that%20the%20talks%20were%20moving%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdespite-mamata-banerjees-snub-seat-talks-with-congress-back-on-sources-5110221%5C%2