hout%20a%20public%20farewell%20within%203%20hours%2C%20or%20Alexey%20will%20be%20buried%20in%20the%20colony.%20She%20refused%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20IC%2C%20as%20they%20are%20not%20authorised%20to%20decide%20how%20and%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20%D0%9A%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%B0%20%D0%AF%D1%80%D0%BC%D1%8B%D1%88%20(%40Kira_Yarmysh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKira_Yarmysh%2Fstatus%2F1761051462837129537%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%2C%20Lyudmila%20Navalnaya%2C%20%26quot%3Brefused%20to%20negotiate%20...%20because%20they%20have%20no%20authority%20to%20decide%20how%20and%20where%20to%20bury%20her%20son%26quot%3B%2C%20Yarmysh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20now%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20alleging%20the%20%26quot%3Bdesecration%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20body%2C%20said%20Ivan%20Zhdanov%2C%20an%20exiled%20ally%20of%20the%20late%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20team%20have%20said%20the%20Kremlin%20is%20%26quot%3Bscared%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20opposition%20leader%20even%20after%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20believe%20the%20authorities%20do%20not%20want%20a%20public%20funeral%20as%20it%20would%20represent%20a%20show%20of%20support%20for%20Navalny's%20movement%20against%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20previously%20called%20Putin%20a%20%26quot%3Bkiller%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20trying%20to%20cover%20his%20tracks%20by%20not%20allowing%20independent%20forensic%20analysis%20of%20Navalny's%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Putin%20is%20scared'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20days%20of%20being%20denied%20access%2C%20Navalny's%20mother%20Lyudmila%20said%20Thursday%20she%20had%20finally%20been%20allowed%20to%20see%20her%20dead%20son's%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20said%20the%20authorities%20were%20not%20willing%20to%20give%20her%20custody%20and%20wanted%20to%20bury%20him%20secretly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2025%20fi