rid's%20portfolio%20now%20consists%20of%2019%20solar%20projects%20across%20eight%20states%20of%20the%20country%20with%20a%20total%20generation%20capacity%20of%201.1%20GWp%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findigrid-acquires-solar-power-plant-at-an-enterprise-value-of-rs-1-550-cr-124022301117_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findigrid-acquires-solar-power-plant-at-an-enterprise-value-of-rs-1-550-cr-124022301117_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findigrid-acquires-solar-power-plant-at-an-enterprise-value-of-rs-1-550-cr-124022301117_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Property%20Purchased%20In%20Homemaker%20Wife's%20Name%20Belongs%20To%20Family%3A%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20held%20that%20a%20property%20purchased%20by%20a%20husband%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20a%20homemaker%20and%20has%20no%20independent%20source%20of%20income%2C%20is%20a%20family%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Arun%20Kumar%20Singh%20Deshwal%20said%20that%20it%20is%20common%20and%20natural%20for%20Hindu%20husbands%20to%20purchase%20properties%20in%20the%20name%20of%20their%20wives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Judge%20was%20hearing%20a%20case%20involving%20a%20son's%20claim%20for%20declaration%20of%20co-ownership%20of%20his%20dead%20father's%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court%20under%20Section%20114%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20may%20presume%20the%20existence%20of%20fact%20that%20the%20property%20purchased%20by%20a%20Hindu%20husband%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20spouse%2C%20who%20is%20a%20homemaker%20and%20does%20not%20have%20an%20independent%20source%20of%20income%2C%20will%20be%20the%20property%20of%20family%2C%20because%20in%20common%20course%20of%20natural%20event%20Hindu%20husband%20purchases%20a%20property%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20homemaker%20and%20does%20not%20have%20any%20source%20of%20income%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20unless%20it%20is%20otherwise%20proved%20that%20the%20property%20was%20purchased%20with%20the%20income%20earned%20by%20the%20wife%2C%20the%20property%20is%20deemed%20to%20have%20been%20purchased%20by%20the%20husband%20using%20his%20own%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appellant%2C%20Saurabh%20Gupta%2C%20the%20son%2C%20had%20filed%20a%20civil%20suit%20seeking%20the%20status%20of%20co-sharer%20of%20one-fourth%20of%20the%20property%20purchased%20by%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20contended%20that%20since%20the%20property%20was%20purchased%20by%20his%20dead%20father%2C%20he%20was%20a%20co-sharer%20in%20it%20along%20with%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20is%20a%20defendant%20in%20the%20suit%20and%20respondent%20in%20the%20present%20appeal%20before%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20property%20was%20purchased%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20mother%2C%20i.e.%2C%20wife%20of%20the%20dead%20father%2C%20the%20appellant%20(son)%20filed%20an%20application%20seeking%20an%20injunction%20(stay)%20against%20the%20transfer%20of%20property%20to%20a%20third%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20statement%2C%20the%20mother%20pleaded%20that%20the%20property%20was%20gifted%20to%20her%20by%20her%20husband%20as%20she%20had%20no%20independent%20source%20of%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20the%20application%20for%20interim%20injunction%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20trial%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowing%20the%20appeal%20filed%20by%20the%20appellant%2C%20the%20high%20court%20in%20its%20February%2015%20judgement%20held%20that%20the%20property%20purchased%20by%20a%20Hindu%20husband%20in%20the%20name%20of%20homemaker%20wife%2C%20without%20any%20independent%20income%2C%20is%20deemed%20to%20have%20been%20purchased%20from%20his%20personal%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20property%2C%20prima%20facie%2C%20becomes%20the%20property%20of%20the%20joint%20Hindu%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20held%20that%20in%20such%20circumstances%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20protect%20the%20property%20from%20creation%20of%20third-party%20rights.%20%26quot%3BIn%20such%20a%20case%2C%20the%20protection%20is%20necessary%20against%20further%20transferring%20the%20property%20or%20changing%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708707960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-01%2F7eom9oh8_allahabad-high-court-ndtv_625x300_07_January_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fproperty-purchased-in-homemaker-wifes-name-belongs-to-family-allahabad-high-court-5114318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20has%20held%20that%20a%20property%20purchased%20by%20a%20husband%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20a%20homemaker%20and%20has%20no%20independent%20source%20of%20income%2C%20is%20a%20family%20property.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fproperty-purchased-in-homemaker-wifes-name-belongs-to-family-allahabad-high-court-5114318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fproperty-purchased-in-homemaker-wifes-name-belongs-to-family-allahabad-high-court-5114318%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fproperty-purchased-in-homemaker-wifes-name-belongs-to-family-allahabad-high-court-5114318%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%