mise%20of%20Darshan%20Singh%2C%20the%20coordinator%20of%20KMM%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%20said%20that%20Darshan%20Singh%20died%20of%20cardiac%20arrest.%20%E2%80%9CDarshan%20Singh%20is%20the%20fourth%20martyr%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%20The%20government%20must%20give%20Rs%205%20lakh%20compensation%20to%20his%20family%2C%20the%20way%20they%20did%20in%20the%20case%20of%20two%20other%20elderly%20farmers%20who%20too%20lost%20their%20lives%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20morcha%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20February%2021%2C%20a%20young%20farmer%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%20reportedly%20died%20of%20a%20bullet%20injury%20while%20protesting%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20border.%20The%20farmers%20had%20announced%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2021%2C%20when%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%20was%20killed%20while%20many%20others%20sustained%20severe%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20family%20of%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%20has%20reportedly%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20ex-gratia%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20a%20government%20job%20to%20his%20sister%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20accept%20the%20ex-gratia%20and%20the%20government%20till%20the%20government%20registers%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20Haryana%20Police.%E2%80%9D%20This%20was%20shared%20by%20one%20of%20Shubhkaran%E2%80%99s%20uncles%2C%20who%20addressed%20the%20media%20on%20this%20issue%20along%20with%20KMM%20leaders%20Jagjeet%20Singh%20Dallewal%20and%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20in%20the%20past%2010%20days%2C%20two%20elderly%20farmers%20namely%20Manjeet%20Singh%20and%20Gyan%20Singh%20had%20lost%20their%20lives%20at%20the%20protest%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanadian%20gurdwaras%20condemn%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20crackdown%20against%20farmer%20activists%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delegation%20of%20the%20British%20Columbia%20gurdwaras%20Council%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Canadian%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20and%20urged%20her%20to%20condemn%20India%E2%80%99s%20violent%20crackdown%20against%20farmer%20activists%20and%20raise%20this%20issue%20with%20the%20High%20Commission%20of%20India%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20council%20members%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20writing%20to%20raise%20concerns%20regarding%20paramilitary%20troop%20mobilization%20at%20Punjab-India%20and%20the%20repression%20of%20farmer%20activists%20in%20recent%20days.%20We%20urge%20you%20to%20immediately%20raise%20this%20issue%20with%20the%20High%20Commission%20of%20India%20in%20Canada%20to%20ensure%20that%20civil%20liberties%20and%20fundamental%20rights%20are%20protected.%20Communities%20across%20Canada%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20possible%20escalation%20of%20violence%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20draconian%20measures%20being%20implemented%20to%20repress%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20democratic%20assembly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15145529%2F9313A034-D5C5-4DE6-A64D-6FDBEE5AE65D-1-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697315%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20photo%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%20Credit%3A%20Photo%3A%20Special%20Arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20council%20members%20mentioned%20that%20since%20February%2013%2C%202024%20farmer%20activists%20from%20across%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20action%20on%20numerous%20policy%20issues%20to%20ensure%20the%20livelihood%20of%20farmers.%20Despite%20written%20commitments%20to%20do%20so%20in%202021%2C%20the%20government%20has%20since%20failed%20to%20take%20any%20concrete%20action%20in%20this%20regard.%20Instead%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20responded%20with%20a%20marked%20escalation%20in%20its%20repression%20of%20political%20dissent-deploying%20drones%2C%20tear%20gas%2C%20live%20ammunition%2C%20incendiary%20devices%2C%20and%20other%20weaponry%20against%20unarmed%20demonstrators.%20One%2021-year-old%20activist%20was%20murdered%20by%20police%20today%20while%20hundreds%20have%20been%20seriously%20injured%20over%20the%20past%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20has%20claimed%20a%20role%20in%20condemning%20human%20rights%20violations%20and%20promoting%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20in%20places%20like%20China%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20elsewhere.%20Canada%20must%20fulfill%20this%20responsibility%20to%20express%20its%20concerns%20with%20India%20as%20well.%20The%20rise%20of%20violent%20xenophobic%20rhetoric%20by%20government%20officials%20and%20unchecked%20mob%20violence%20targeting%20Sikhs%2C%20Muslims%20and%20other%20minorities%20continues%20to%20increase%20day%20by%20day%2C%20raising%20alarm%20amongst%20numerous%20experts%20about%20the%20real%20possibilities%20of%20renewed%20genocidal%20violence%20in%20the%20sub-continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20murder%20of%20Bhai%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20by%20Indian%20agents%20in%20Canada%20demonstrates%20that%20continued%20impunity%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20accountability%20only%20serves%20to%20embolden%20the%20Indian%20regime%20in%20its%20violent%20repression%20of%20minorities%20and%20political%20dissidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUK%20MP%20raises%20voice%20against%20the%20killing%20of%20farmer%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20February%2022%2C%202024%2C%20the%20UK%E2%80%99s%20first%20Sikh%20MP%20Tanmanjeet%20Singh%20Dhesi%20also%20raised%20his%20voice%20against%20the%20killing%20of%2021-year-old%20young%20farmer%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%20from%20Balloh%20village%2C%20Bathinda%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhesi%20is%20known%20for%20raising%20his%20voice%20against%20human%20rights%20abuses.%20During%20the%20previous%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20protest%20in%202021%2C%20Dhesi%20had%20called%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20UK%20parliament%20to%20discuss%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20against%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%2C%20Dhesi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20my%20Slough%20constituents%2C%20including%20members%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20and%20local%20gurdwaras%20have%20written%20to%20me%20regarding%20their%20safety%20concerns%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20protesting%20farmers%20in%20their%20attempt%20to%20march%20towards%20the%20Indian%20capital%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20Yesterday%2C%20a%20protester%20was%20killed%20during%20a%20reported%20standoff%20with%20the%20police%2C%20wherein%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20and%20I%20quote%3B%20%E2%80%9Ca%20bullet%20wound%20to%20the%20head.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhesi%20further%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Punjab%20Health%20Minister%20confirmed%20that%20a%20second%20boy%20had%20also%20sustained%20a%20bullet%20wound%2C%20but%20luckily%2C%20he%20has%20survived%2C%20with%20another%2013%20being%20treated%20for%20injuries%20in%20hospitals.%20And%20today%2C%20the%20BBC%20have%20reported%20that%20X%2C%20Twitter%2C%20admitted%20to%20being%20compelled%20against%20their%20wishes%20to%20take%20down%20legitimate%20posts%20and%20accounts%20of%20activists.%20So%20does%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20agree%20with%20me%20that%