%20to%20the%20lion%20named%20%E2%80%98Akbar%E2%80%99%20as%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbengal-vishwa-hindu-parishad-sita-akbar-lion%5C%22%3Ehurt%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20Hindus.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20advocate%20general%20(AAG)%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20lions%20had%20been%20named%20in%20Tripura%20and%20that%20it%20was%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Tripura%20Zoo%20authorities%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fcalcutta-high-court%2Fcalcutta-high-court-directs-vhps-plea-against-lioness-named-sita-to-be-reclassified-as-pil-state-submits-naming-took-place-at-tripura-zoo-250197%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bhattacharya%20remarked%20that%20this%20controversy%20could%20have%20been%20avoided.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20has%20given%20this%20name%3F%20Causing%20controversy%3F%20I%20was%20thinking%20whether%20any%20animal%20can%20be%20given%20a%20name%20after%20a%20god%2C%20mythological%20hero%2C%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20or%20Nobel%20laureate.%20You%20are%20a%20welfare%20state%20and%20it%20is%20a%20secular%20state.%20Why%20should%20you%20draw%20controversy%20by%20naming%20a%20lion%20after%20Sita%20and%20Akbar%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20Sita%2C%20but%20I%20also%20don%E2%80%99t%20support%20the%20naming%20of%20a%20lion%2C%20Akbar.%20He%20was%20a%20very%20efficient%20and%20noble%20Mughal%20emperor.%20Very%20successful%20and%20secular%20Mughal%20emperor.%20If%20it%20is%20already%20named%2C%20the%20state%20authority%20should%20shun%20it%20and%20avoid%20it.%20West%20Bengal%20should%20have%20challenged%20the%20names%20given%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20concerns%20about%20potential%20religious%20controversies%2C%20the%20Bench%20urged%20the%20state%20to%20consider%20renaming%20the%20lioness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pro