Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20concluded%20her%20speech%20with%20a%20request%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BStop%20coming%20after%20us%20and%20let%20my%20Kashmir%20community%20live%20in%20peace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20over%20a%20million%20views%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20Yana%20Mir%20in%20her%20reply%20to%20the%20video%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Malala%20theory%20was%20given%20to%20her%20by%20her%20sister%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mir%20received%20the%20Diversity%20Ambassador%20Award%20from%20UK%20MP%20Theresa%20Villiers%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Bob%20Blackman%20and%20Virendra%20Sharma%2C%20both%20MPs%20in%20the%20Parliament.%20Virendra%20Sharma%20is%20a%20British-Indian%20MP%20from%20the%20opposition%20Labour%20MP%20from%20Ealing%20Southhall%20near%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20users%20including%20actor%20Anupam%20Kher%2C%20congratulated%20Ms%20Mir%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Study%20Centre%20(JKSC)%2C%20UK%2C%20hosted%20'India's%20Sankalp%20Divas'%20at%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20in%20the%20Parliament%20in%20London.%20JKSC%20is%20a%20think%20tank%20that%20is%20dedicated%20to%20studying%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20issues%20surrounding%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mir%2C%20in%20her%20speech%2C%20said%20on%20'Sankalp%20Divas'%20she%20hopes%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20perpetrators%20living%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20Pakistan%20would%20stop%20maligning%20my%20country%20in%20international%20media%20and%20human%20rights%20forums%2C%20stop%20unwanted%20selective%20outrage%20remotely%20from%20their%20cosy%20UK%20homes...Stop%20coming%20after%20us...thousands%20of%20Kashmiri%20mothers%20have%20lost%20their%20sons%20because%20of%20the%20dark%20hole%20of%20terrorism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708703760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fnuodehto_yana-mir_625x300_23_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fim-not-a-malala-im-free-in-india-kashmiri-journalist-in-uk-parliament-5114641%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yana%20Mir%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20and%20a%20journalist%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20honoured%20in%20the%20UK%20Parliament%20with%20the%20Diversity%20Ambassador%20award.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fim-not-a-malala-im-free-in-india-kashmiri-journalist-in-uk-parliament-5114641%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fim-not-a-malala-im-free-in-india-kashmiri-journalist-in-uk-parliament-5114641%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fim-not-a-malala-im-free-in-india-kashmiri-journalist-in-uk-parliament-5114641%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20CBI%20Red%20Flags%2050%25%20Of%20Nursing%20Colleges%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Changes%20Rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20amended%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20requirements%20to%20establish%20a%20nursing%20college.%20Under%20new%20rules%20for%202024%2C%20an%20institution%20needs%20at%20least%208%2C150%20square%20feet%20of%20space.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20massive%20downgrade%20from%20existing%20rules%2C%20which%20say%20that%20it%20needs%20at%20least%2019%2C060%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20Indian%20Nursing%20Council%20mandates%20at%20least%2023%2C720%20square%20feet%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20other%20requisites%20like%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20faculty%20members%2C%20a%20canteen%20and%20a%20library%2C%20and%20a%20100-bed%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20five%20months%20after%20NDTV%20reported%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20many%20such%20institutions%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20the%20CBI%20is%20already%20probing%20over%20600%20after%20many%20were%20found%20without%20proper%20faculty%20or%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20visited%20one%20'college'%20-%20the%20Savita%20Institute%20Of%20Health%20Science%20in%20Bhopal's%20Data%20Colony%20-%20and%20found%20it%20was%20being%20run%20out%20of%20three%20rooms%20on%20one%20floor%20of%20a%20three-storey%20residential%20building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'college'%2C%20run%20by%20NM%20Srivastava%20-%20a%20former%20director%20of%20medical%20education%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20-%20offers%20a%20Bachelors%20degree%20and%20a%20diploma%20course.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fi7e66c4_nursing-_625x300_23_February_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInquiries%20into%20other%20'colleges'%20found%20one%20faculty%20member%20taught%20at%2010%20across%20three%20cities%20-%20as%20the%20principal%20in%20some%20and%20an%20associate%20professor%20in%20others.%20Investigating%20agencies%20have%20made%20similarly%20disturbing%20discoveries%2C%20including%20'colleges'%20with%20no%20faculty%20that%20just%20hand%20out%20'certificates'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Ground%20Report%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fground-report-a-3-room-nursing-college-in-madhya-pradesh-exposes-a-larger-problem-4456818%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3-Room%20Nursing%20College%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Exposes%20A%20Larger%20Problem%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENineteen%20such%20institutes%20were%20de-recognised%20in%20August%2C%20after%20which%20the%20state%20authorised%20the%20CBI%20to%20examine%20all%20institutions%20registered%20in%202020%2F21.%20Per%20the%20latest%20update%20on%20this%20investigation%2C%20nearly%2050%20per%20cent%20(of%20670)%20have%20been%20declared%20ineligible%2C%20prompting%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20to%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivist%20Vishal%20Baghel%20told%20NDTV%20he%20plans%20to%20challenge%20these%20rules%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20earlier%20released%20the%20names%20of%20all%20308%20institutions%20investigated%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20result%20of%20each%20investigation%3B%20i.e.%2C%20with%20the%20tags%20'suitable'%2C%20'deficient'%2C%20or%20'unstable'%20in%20front%20of%20their%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20this%20list%2C%20even%20a%20state%20government%20institution%20in%20Rewa%20was%20found%20unsuitable.%20The%20CBI%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20only%20169%20colleges%20investigated%20so%20far%20met%20the%20requirements.%20On%20the%20CBI's%20'red%20list'%20is%20Savita%20Nursing%20Institute%2C%20which%20was%20started%20in%202015%2F16%20and%20has%20seen%20at%20least%20four%20batches%20of%20students%20'graduate'%2C%20raising%20serious%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20had%20sought%20permission%20from%20the%20High%20Court%20to%20start%20the%20process%20of%20recognition%20for%202024%2F25%20and%20this%20permission%20has%20been%20given.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708703280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fjgoglet_mp-nursing-college-650_625x300_06_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-nursing-colleges-cbi-after-cbi-red-flags-50-of-nursing-colleges-madhya-pradesh-changes-rules-5114604%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20amended%20requirements%20for%20recognition%20of%20a%20nursing%20educational%20institution%20so%20that%20it%20is%20in%20line%20with%20those%20set%20by%20the%20Nursing%20Council%20of%20India%2C%20after%20an%20NDTV%20ground%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-nursing-colleges-cbi-after-cbi-red-flags-50-of-nursing-colleges-madhya-pradesh-changes-rules-5114604%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3