-inevitable-removal-from-office-13079183%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20and%20a%20half%20months%20after%20the%20fighting%20began%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20finally%20made%20public%20a%20draft%20of%20his%20vision%20for%20Gaza%20after%20the%20war%20finishes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A236%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnetanyahus-gaza-plan-appears-to-be-attempt-to-delay-inevitable-removal-from-office-13079183%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnetanyahus-gaza-plan-appears-to-be-attempt-to-delay-inevitable-removal-from-office-13079183%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnetanyahus-gaza-plan-appears-to-be-attempt-to-delay-inevitable-removal-from-office-13079183%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Refrain%20from%20Any%20Sort%20of%20Complicity%20with%20Israel'%3A%20Indians%20for%20Palestine%20Group%20to%20Modi%20Govt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11160252%2FGA6xi9-WoAEKSsS.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndians%20for%20Palestine%20has%20called%20on%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20to%20publicly%20endorse%20the%20latest%20ruling%20of%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20to%20stand%20against%20all%20violations%20of%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20refrain%20from%20%E2%80%9Cany%20sort%20of%20complicity%20with%20Israel%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemanding%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Palestine%2C%20the%20group%20said%20it%20is%20dismayed%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpassivity%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20its%20refusal%20to%20forthrightly%20condemn%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20inhuman%20assault%20on%20Gaza%20and%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnlike%20many%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20that%20are%20re-assessing%20their%20relations%20with%20Israel%2C%20India%20continues%20its%20close%20collaboration%20with%20it%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20defence%20and%20surveillance%20sectors.%20It%20is%20deeply%20disturbing%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20to%20learn%20from%20recent%20media%20reports%20that%20amid%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20war%20on%20Gaza%2C%20twenty%20Hermes-900%20military%20drones%20produced%20jointly%20by%20Adani-Elbit%20Advanced%20Systems%20India%20Ltd.%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20Israel%20for%20possible%20deployment%20in%20Gaza.%20Many%20other%20Indian%20companies%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20subsidized%20joint%20ventures%20with%20Israeli%20weapons%20manufacturers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20group%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20exert%20pressure%20on%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20follow%20the%20ICJ%20ruling%20on%20Gaza%20and%20condemn%20Israeli%20actions%2C%20the%20group%20held%20a%20meeting%20at%20the%20Constitution%20Club%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Friday%2C%20February%2023.%20The%20meeting%20was%20attended%20by%20representatives%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20media%2C%20diplomatic%20community%2C%20legal%20profession%2C%20foreign%20policy%20experts%2C%20among%20several%20hundred%20participants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20government%20is%20also%20facilitating%20the%20recruitment%20of%20Indian%20workers%20in%20replacement%20of%20Palestinian%20workers%20whose%20work%20permits%20are%20now%20suspended.%20This%20move%20is%20objectionable%20not%20just%20in%20its%20support%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20decision%20against%20Palestinian%20workers%20but%20also%20in%20its%20indifference%20to%20the%20possible%20dangers%20facing%20Indian%20workers%20being%20sent%20to%20Israel.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20further%20played%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20Israel%20by%20suppressing%20all%20attempts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20unfolding%20genocide%20in%20Gaza%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20group%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20statement%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERESOLUTION%20AND%20STATEMENT%20OF%20SOLIDARITY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cu%3EINTERNATIONAL%20COURT%20AND%20JUSTICE%20FOR%20GAZA%3A%3C%2Fu%3E%20%3Cu%3EA%20PUBLIC%20MEETING%20ON%20THE%20ICJ%20RULING%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(New%20Delhi%2C%2023%20February%202024)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20January%2011%2C%202024%2C%20the%20daily%20death%20rate%20in%20Gaza%20was%20higher%20than%20in%20any%20other%20major%2021st-century%20conflict.%20The%20death%20toll%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20assault%20on%20Gaza%20has%20now%20crossed%2029%2C000%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20and%20children%2C%20with%20over%2070%2C000%20Gazans%20wounded.%20Among%20those%20killed%20are%20approximately%2085%20journalists%20and%20media%20workers%2C%20152%20UN%20workers%2C%20600%20health%20workers%20and%2012%2C000%20children.%20The%20long-term%20impacts%20of%20this%20continuing%20massacre%20go%20far%20beyond%20the%20immediate%20casualties%3A%20deepening%20poverty%2C%20severe%20water%20crisis%2C%20the%20shutdown%20of%20healthcare%20systems%2C%20and%20chronic%20trauma.%20According%20to%20international%20experts%2C%20the%20victims%20of%20starvation%20and%20disease%20in%20Gaza%20may%20exceed%20the%20number%20of%20those%20killed%20directly%20during%20Israeli%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2026%2C%202024%2C%20in%20response%20to%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20application%20against%20Israel%20for%20violating%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20in%20its%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%2C%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20(ICJ)%20ruled%20that%20Israel%20must%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20all%20measures%20within%20its%20power%E2%80%9D%20to%20prevent%20such%20actions.%20This%20ruling%20is%20of%20historic%20significance%20because%20it%20is%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20highest%20court%20has%20held%20Israel%20culpable%20for%20its%20violations%20of%20international%20human%20rights%20laws%20concerning%20Palestinians.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20ICJ%20has%20deemed%20the%20arguments%20from%20South%20Africa%20as%20substantiating%20a%20plausible%20claim%20of%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20landmark%20order%20of%20the%20ICJ%20also%20imposes%20a%20moral%20and%20legal%20obligation%20on%20other%20country%20members%20of%20the%20ICJ%20and%20signatories%20of%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20including%20India%2C%20to%20cease%20funding%20or%20facilitating%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20actions.%20The%20signatories%20to%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20are%20obligated%20to%20prevent%20genocide%2C%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20genocide%2C%20incitement%20to%20commit%20genocide%20and%20complicity%20in%20genocide.%20They%20risk%20transgressing%20the%20Convention%20if%20there%20is%20no%20reprimanding%20of%2C%20or%20suspension%20of%20economic-cultural-social%20relations%20with%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20a%20member%20country%20now%20being%20tried%20for%20genocide.%20Such%20is%20the%20devastation%20already%20caused%20by%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actions%20that%20there%20is%20a%20moral%20responsibility%20on%20all%20signatories%20to%20the%20Convention%20to%20unequivocally%20oppose%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20continuing%20onslaught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa%20of%20South%20Africa%20declared%20in%20a%20statement%20on%208%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20February%20that%20given%20his%20country%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20as%20a%20nation%20that%20has%20fought%20and%20defeated%20Apartheid%2C%20it%20has%20a%20particular%20obligation%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20people%20everywhere.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20remember%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20has%20also%20been%20one%20of%20opposing%20Apartheid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20shared%20stance%2C%20we%20are%20dismayed%20to%20note%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20passivity%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20its%20refusal%20to%20forthrightly%20condemn%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20inhuman%20assault%20on%20Gaza%20and%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20Unlike%20many%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20that%20are%20re-assessing%20their%20relations%20with%20Israel%2C%20India%20continues%20its%20close%20collaboration%20with%20it%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20defence%20and%20surveillance%20sectors.%20It%20is%20deeply%20disturbing%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20to%20learn%20from%20recent%20media%20reports%20that%20amid%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20war%20on%20Gaza%2C%20twenty%20Hermes-900%20military%20drones%20produced%20jointly%20by%20Adani-Elbit%20Advanced%20Systems%20India%20Ltd.%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20Israel%20for%20possible%20deployment%20in%20Gaza.%20Many%20other%20Indian%20companies%20are%20also%20involved%20in%20subsidized%20joint%20ventures%20with%20Israeli%20weapons%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20is%20also%20facilitating%20the%20recruitment%20of%20Indian%20workers%20in%20replacement%20of%20Palestinian%20workers%20whose%20work%20permits%20are%20now%20suspended.%20This%20move%20is%20objectionable%20not%20just%20in%20its%20support%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20decision%20against%20Palestinian%20workers%20but%20also%20in%20its%20indifference%20to%20the%20possible%20dangers%20facing%20Indian%20workers%20being%20sent%20to%20Israel.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20further%20played%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20Israel%20by%20suppressing%20all%20attempts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20unfolding%20genocide%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20thus%20call%20upon%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20publicly%20endorse%20the%20latest%20ruling%20of%20the%20ICJ%2C%20stand%20against%20all%20violations%20of%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20and%20refrain%20from%20any%20sort%20of%20complicity%20with%20Israel.%20We%20demand%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20further%20call%20on%20people%20across%20Asia%20to%20demonstrate%20collective%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine%20%E2%80%93%20in%20spirit%2C%20resources%2C%20speech%2C%20and%20action.%20We%20particularly%20welcome%20the%20recent%20decision%20of%20the%20Water%20Transport%20Workers%20Federation%20of%20India%20%E2%80%93%20representing%203%2C500%20workers%20at%2011%20major%20Indian%20ports%20%E2%80%93%20to%20refuse%20any%20cooperation%20with%20the%20loading%20or%20unloading%20of%20%E2%80%9Cweaponized%20cargoes%20from%20Israel%20or%20any%20other%20country%20which%20could%20handle%20military%20equipment%20and%20its%20allied%20cargo%20for%20war%20in%20Palestine%E2%80%9D.%20Many%20other%20steps%20can%20be%20taken%20to%20express%20support%20for%20Palestine%2C%20including%20the%20submission%20of%20photo%2Fvideo%20evidence%20of%20ongoing%20war%20crimes%20(accessed%20through%20verified%20accounts%20of%20Palestinian%20journalists)%20through%20the%20online%20portal%20of%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court.%20We%20should%20not%20be%20left%20behind%20as%20mass%20protests%20are%20sweeping%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EStand%20for%20Palestine!%20Stand%20for%20Humanity!%20Ceasefire%20Now!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94-%20%3Cem%3EIndians%20for%20Palestine%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20group%20of%20concerned%20citizens)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708700347000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11160252%2FGA6xi9-WoAEKSsS.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frefrain-from-any-sort-of-complicity-with-israel-indians-for-palestine-group-to-modi-govt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Demanding%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20in%20Palestine%2C%20the%20group%20said%20it%20is%20dismayed%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20'passivity'%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20its%20refusal%20to%20forthrightly%20condemn%20I