.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-11-at-10.44.57-AM-1708690690-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-11-at-10.44.57-AM-1708690690-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-11-at-10.44.57-AM-1708690690-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343016%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20is%20a%20century-old%20one%20that%20is%20made%20with%20wood%20and%20stone%20and%20can%20withstand%20earthquakes%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Kundan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20century-old%20pride%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20on%20his%20way%20home%20from%20the%20farm%2C%20Kundan%20saw%20an%20unusual%20sight.%20A%20group%20of%20eight%20tourists%20with%20their%20luggage%20was%20waiting%20near%20the%20bus%20stop.%20It%20was%20past%20six%20in%20the%20evening.%20%E2%80%9CBuses%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286607%2Ffriends-quit-job-to-build-ecofriendly-home-stay-for-weekend-getaway-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20village%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20not%20ply%20post%20six%20o%E2%80%99clock.%20I%20knew%20there%20was%20no%20way%20for%20the%20tourists%20to%20reach%20Kullu%20before%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kundan%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20conversation%20later%2C%20Kundan%20was%20seen%20leading%20the%20group%20of%20tourists%20towards%20his%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%20enjoyed%20their%20stay%20in%20the%20mud%20home%20and%20one%20among%20the%20group%20coaxed%20Kundan%20to%20have%20his%20house%20registered%20on%20a%20travel%20website.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20helped%20me%20with%20everything.%20And%20once%20they%20left%2C%20I%20began%20getting%20requests%20from%20people%20across%20India%20who%20wanted%20to%20experience%20life%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282723%2Fbest-homestays-in-ladakh-things-to-do-in-leh-local-experience%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emud%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20time%20to%20come%2C%20Kundan%20built%20an%20additional%20room%20beside%20the%20homestay%20where%20travellers%20who%20were%20not%20comfortable%20with%20living%20in%20a%20mud%20property%2C%20could%20stay.%20By%202016%2C%20Kundan%20and%20his%20family%20had%20become%20pros%20at%20hosting%20guests%20not%20just%20from%20India%20but%20Australia%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20Philippines%20and%20Italy%2C%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20story%20that%20the%20farmer%20treats%20each%20of%20his%20guests%20to%2C%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280532%2Fchildhood-friends-convert-grandmothers-house-into-eco-friendly-homestay-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesign%20philosophy%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20home.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20standing%20tall%20for%20over%20a%20century.%20Not%20an%20earthquake%20has%20been%20able%20to%20shift%20its%20foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%20This%20remarkable%20fact%20is%20courtesy%20of%20the%20home%E2%80%99s%20architecture%2C%20which%20is%20built%20in%20a%20traditional%20style%20using%20wood%20and%20stone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fhimachal-homestay-1708690887.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kundan's%20wife%20Kala%20cooks%20a%20pahadi%20feast%20using%20the%20produce%20they%20grow%20on%20the%20land%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F