r%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finteragencystandingcommittee.org%2Fthe-inter-agency-standing-committee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprincipals%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Inter-Agency%20Standing%20Committee%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finteragencystandingcommittee.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIASC%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20the%20coordinating%20body%20of%20global%20humanitarian%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDiseases%20are%20rampant.%20Famine%20is%20looming.%20Water%20is%20at%20a%20trickle.%20Basic%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20decimated.%20Food%20production%20has%20come%20to%20a%20halt.%20Hospitals%20have%20turned%20into%20battlefields.%20One%20million%20children%20face%20daily%20traumas%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20noted%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finteragencystandingcommittee.org%2Finter-agency-standing-committee%2Fstatement-principals-inter-agency-standing-committee-civilians-gaza-extreme-peril-while-world%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%E2%80%98death%20blow%E2%80%99%20to%20aid%20efforts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20particularly%20dire%20in%20Rafah%2C%20at%20the%20far%20south%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRafah%2C%20the%20latest%20destination%20for%20well%20over%20one%20million%20displaced%2C%20hungry%20and%20traumatised%20people%20crammed%20into%20a%20small%20sliver%20of%20land%2C%20has%20become%20another%20battleground%20in%20this%20brutal%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20IASC%20heads%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFurther%20escalation%20of%20violence%20in%20this%20densely%20populated%20area%20would%20cause%20mass%20casualties.%20It%20could%20also%20deal%20a%20death%20blow%20to%20a%20humanitarian%20response%20that%20is%20already%20on%20its%20knees%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumanitarians%20at%20risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IASC%20principals%20highlighted%20the%20risks%20aid%20workers%20face%20daily%20in%20their%20efforts%20to%20help%20people%20in%20desperate%20need%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20can%20%E2%80%9Conly%20do%20so%20much.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHumanitarian%20workers%2C%20themselves%20displaced%20and%20facing%20shelling%2C%20death%2C%20movement%20restrictions%20and%20a%20breakdown%20of%20civil%20order%2C%20continue%20efforts%20to%20deliver%20to%20those%20in%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20faced%20with%20so%20many%20obstacles%20%E2%80%93%20including%20safety%20and%20movement%20restrictions%20%E2%80%93%20they%20can%20only%20do%20so%20much.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20essentials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20principals%20underscored%20that%20no%20amount%20of%20humanitarian%20response%20will%20make%20up%20for%20the%20months%20of%20deprivation%20that%20families%20in%20Gaza%20have%20endured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20effort%20to%20salvage%20the%20humanitarian%20operation%20so%20that%20we%20can%20provide%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20the%20bare%20essentials%3A%20medicine%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20food%20and%20shelter%20as%20temperatures%20plummet%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%2C%20they%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%2010%20indispensable%20elements%3A%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%3B%20protection%20of%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20infrastructure%3B%20immediate%20release%20of%20hostages%3B%20reliable%20entry%20points%20for%20aid%3B%20security%20assurances%20and%20unimpeded%20access%3B%20a%20functioning%20humanitarian%20notification%20system%3B%20roads%20cleared%20of%20explosive%20ordnance%3B%20and%20a%20stable%20communication%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20they%20called%20for%20the%20UN%20agency%20assisting%20Palestine%20refugees%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20receive%20the%20resources%20it%20needs%20to%20provide%20life-saving%20assistance%20as%20well%20as%20a%20halt%20to%20campaigns%20seeking%20to%20discredit%20the%20UN%20and%20NGOs%20doing%20their%20best%20to%20save%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20calling%20on%20Israel%20to%20fulfil%20its%20legal%20obligation%2C%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20and%20human%20rights%20law%2C%20to%20provide%20food%20and%20medical%20supplies%20and%20facilitate%20aid%20operations%2C%20and%20on%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20to%20prevent%20an%20even%20worse%20catastrophe%20from%20happening%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20humanitarian%20leaders%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146837%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20UN%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708689616000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28140819%2FGEw1UHwXMAEPdVM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdiseases-are-rampant-famine-is-looming-humanitarian-leaders-unite-in-urgent-plea-for-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Water%20is%20at%20a%20trickle.%20Basic%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20decimated.%20Food%20production%20has%20come%20to%20a%20halt.%20One%20million%20children%20face%20daily%20traumas%2C'%20said%20the%20principals%20of%20the%20Inter-Agency%20Standing%20Committee%2C%20the%20coordinating%20body%20of%20global%20humanitarian%20organisations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdiseases-are-rampant-famine-is-looming-humanitarian-leaders-unite-in-urgent-plea-for-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20approves%20500%20new%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708689461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107945141%2Cimgsize-897587.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-imposes-500-new-sanctions-on-russia-white-house%2Farticleshow%2F107945137.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107945137.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPresident%20Biden%20announced%20500%20more%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%20for%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20death%20of%20Alexei%20Navalny.%20The%20United%20States%20will%20impose%20export%20restrictions%20on%20nearly%20100%20entities%20and%20implement%20measures%20to%20diminish%20Russia's%20energy%20revenues.%20The%20sanctions%20will%20target%20sanctions%20violators%2C%20Russia's%20financial%20sector%2C%20defense%20industry%2C%20and%20procurement%20networks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20News%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-imposes-500-new-sanctions-on-russia-white-house%2Farticleshow%2F107945137.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-imposes-500-new-sanctions-on-russia-white-house%2Famp_articleshow%2F107945137.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-imposes-500-new-sanctions-on-russia-white-house%2Famp_articleshow%2F107945137.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Economy%3A%20Down%20the%20Rabbit%20Hole%20and%20Beyond%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23160306%2Fprasoon-srivastav-vDfkrGeRXRE-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20significant%20general%20elections%20in%202024.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20world%20will%20be%20watching%20as%20the%20largest%20democratic%20festival%20plays%20itself%20out.%20This%20will%20undoubtedly%20have%20profound%20implications%20for%20the%20geopolitical%20order%2C%20perhaps%20even%20more%20so%20than%20the%20US%20presidential%20elections.%20The%20world%20knows%20China%E2%80%99s%20economy%20is%20faltering%3B%20therefore%2C%20it%20will%20closely%20look%20towards%20India%20as%20the%20next%20big%20economic%20force.%20There%20has%20been%20growing%20optimism%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%2C%20but%20there%20is%20one%20state%20that%20is%20pulling%20India%20down.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(UP)%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20states%2C%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20poorly%20performing%20economies%20in%20the%20north%20and%20the%20east%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20recorded%20a%20per%20capita%20Net%20State%20Domestic%20Product%20of%20Rs%2070%2C792%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%202021-22.%20With%20a%20population%20roughly%20equivalent%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20200%20million%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20economic%20disparity%20becomes%20stark.%20Despite%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20economy%20teetering%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20collapse%20due%20to%20democratic%20setbacks%20and%20sluggish%20growth%2C%20its%20per%20capita%20income%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20World%20Bank%20data%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.worldbank.org%2Findicator%2FNY.GDP.PCAP.CD%3Flocations%3DPK%5C%22%3Estands%20at%20%241%2C588.9%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20nearly%20double%20that%20of%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20many%20know%20this%20grim%20reality%3A%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20not%20only%20trails%20behind%20Pakistan%20but%20also%20lags%20behind%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%2C%20renowned%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20poorest%20regions.%20World%20Bank%20Open%20Data%20indicates%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20(excluding%20high%20income)%20per%20capita%20income%20at%20current%20US%24%20is%20%241700.1%20in%202022.%20While%20some%20economists%20argue%20that%20per%20capita%20income%20alone%20fails%20to%20fully%20encapsulate%20a%20region%E2%80%99s%20economic%20standing%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20undeniable%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20economic%20condition%20falls%20significantly%20short%20of%20optimal%20levels.%20For%20example%2C%20Noida%20plays%20a%20big%20role%20in%20increasing%20the%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20UP.%20The%20per%20capita%20income%20simply%20does%20not%20mean%20all%20citizens%20of%20UP%20are%20earning%20Rs%2070%2C792%20per%20year.%20Per%20capita%20income%20is%20calculated%20by%20taking%20the%20ratio%20of%20the%20total%20income%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20total%20population%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fundamental%20flaw%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20economy%20lies%20in%20its%20entrenched%20feudal%20system%2C%20where%20the%20state%20lords%20over%20cattle%2C%20women%2C%20marginalised%20communities%20and%20minorities.%20The%20pervasive%20presence%20of%20the%20so-called%20mafia%20raj%2C%20along%20with%20frequent%20brutalities%20such%20as%20gang%20rape%20and%20violence%2C%20has%20tainted%20UP%E2%80%99s%20reputation.%20Consequently%2C%20when%20the%20chief%20minister%20convenes%20an%20investor%20summit%2C%20prominent%20business%20leaders%20may%20attend%20and%20sign%20Memorandums%20of%20Understanding%2C%20yet%20the%20conversion%20rate%20remains%20abysmal.%20In%20essence%2C%20these%20investors%2C%20gripped%20by%20apprehension%20regarding%20the%20current%20administration%2C%20may%20momentarily%20commit%2C%20but%20they%20rarely%20follow%20through%20with%20the%20initiation%20or%20actualisation%20of%20commercial%20projects%20in%20UP.%20The%20share%20of%20industrial%20sector%20in%20gross%20value%20added%20has%20been%20decreasing.%20From%202012-17%2C%20the%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20the%20industrial%20sector%20has%20been%209.9%25%20and%20from%202017-22%2C%20it%20declined%20to%20a%20mere%200.6%25.%20In%20terms%20of%20number%20of%20factories%2C%20Bihar%20saw%20a%20100.4%25%20increase%2C%20Haryana%20saw%20a%20159%25%20increase%2C%20Assam%20saw%20a%20200%25%20increase%20while%20UP%20saw%20an%20increase%20of%20only%2069%25%20from%20the%20period%202004-05%20to%202019-20.%20The%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20failure%20to%20redistribute%20land%20and%20dismal%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20has%20apparently%20made%20UP%20an%20economic%20wasteland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20facet%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20predicament%20manifests%20in%20the%20relentless%20scourge%20of%20poverty.%20The%20state%20has%20nearly%2023%25%20of%20population%20who%20are%20multidimensionally%20poor.%20Just%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20three%20districts%20of%20UP%20namely%20Bahraich%2C%20Balrampur%2C%20Shravasti%20were%20in%20the%20headlines%20for%20recording%20a%2070%25%20poverty%20rate.%20As%20per%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-08%2FIndia-National-Multidimentional-Poverty-Index-2023.pdf%5C%22%3ENITI%20Aayog%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20Bahraich%20has%20more%2050%25%20population%20who%20are%20multidimensionally%20poor.%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20life%20expectancy%2C%20at%2066%20years%2C%20parallels%20that%20of%20African%20nations%20like%20Ethiopia%20and%20Gabon.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rbi.org.in%2Fscripts%2FAnnualPublications.aspx%3Fhead%3DHandbook%2Bof%2BStatistics%2Bon%2BIndian%2BStates%5C%22%3ERBI%20Handbook%20of%20Indian%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20stands%20at%2038%20per%201%2C000%20in%202020%2C%20the%20maternal%20mortality%20rate%20stands%20at%20167%20per%201%2C00%2C000%20live%20births%20and%2045.6%25%20of%20pregnant%20women%20aged%20between%2015-45%20and%2066%25%20of%20children%20of%20aged%20between%206-59%20months%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1795421%5C%22%3Eare%20anaemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Despite%20the%20touted%20%E2%80%9Cdemographic%20dividend%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20grotesque%20reality%20is%20when%2050.4%25%20of%20the%20female%20population%20aged%20between%2015-49%20years%20are%20anaemic%2C%20the%20prospect%20of%20any%20dividend%20is%20risible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20delve%20into%20the%20growth%20rate.%20The%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20has%20made%20the%20bold%20claim%20of%20a%20%241%20trillion%20economy.%20It%20is%20conventionally%20believed%20that%20states%20with%20a%20lower%20initial%20economic%20base%20possess%20higher%20potential%20for%20growth.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20poorer%20a%20state%2C%20the%20faster%20it%20can%20advance%20economically%2C%20thereby%20gaining%20increased%20access%20to%20funds%20within%20the%20Indian%20Union.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradesh-economy-comparison-with-tamil-nadu-south-india%2Farticle67821390.ece%5C%22%3EFor%20example%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20UP%20receives%20Rs%202.73%20back%20for%20every%20Re%201%20it%20contributes%20to%20the%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20while%20Tamil%20Nadu%20receives%20only%2029%20paisa%20for%20every%20Re%201%20it%20contributes%20to%20the%20Union.%20Perhaps%20an%20argument%20could%20be%20made%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20working%20more%20towards%20funding%20the%20freebies%20of%20UP%2C%20but%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20objectivity%2C%20I%20would%20focus%20solely%20on%20UP.%20The%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Flucknow-news%2Fups-gsdp-shrinks-5-9-per-cent-in-202021-101632161467657.html%5C%22%3EUP%E2%80%99s%20Gross%20State%20Domestic%20Product%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20current%20prices%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fdid-up-economy-do-better-under-akhilesh-than-yogi-a-data-check-on-states-1-trillion-ambition%2F1627925%2F%5C%22%3E%20has%20been%208.28%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20period%202016-17%20to%202021-22%2C%20as%20per%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Economics%20and%20Statistics%2C%20GOUP%20(Government%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh).%20To%20achieve%20a%20%241%20trillion%20target%20in%20five%20years%2C%20UP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradesh-election-adityanath-economic-performance%5C%22%3Eneeds%20to%20grow%20by%2032%25%20per%20annum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20is%20no%20harm%20in%20having%20the%20audacity%20of%20ambition%2C%20but%20truth%20be%20told%2C%20spaceships%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20lit%20up%20by%20candles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lamentable%20part%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20that%20the%20voters%20are%20completely%20agnostic%20about%20the%20democratic%20power%20they%20posses%20to%20bring%20in%20an%20economic%20transformation.%20The%20poor%20voters%20are%20failing%20to%20grasp%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20voting%20for%20forces%20that%20are%20further%20disenfranchising%20them.%20The%20result%20of%20this%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Futtar-pradesh-began-declining-after-1980s-old-industrial-cities-played-big-role%2F710784%2F%5C%22%3EUP%20has%20become%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20purgatory%20of%20prosperity%20and%20a%20geography%20of%20maladies.%20The%20economy%20cannot%20be%20drastically%20upscaled%20unless%20there%20is%20massive%20democratic%20reform%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20steady%20shrinkage%20of%20democratic%20spaces%2C%20laceration%20of%20institutional%20autonomy%2C%20the%20focus%20on%20cults%20need%20to%20stop.%20Income%2C%20quality%20of%20living%20needs%20to%20be%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20discourse%20replacing%20caste%20and%20cult.%20In%20a%20conservative%20democratic%20milieu%2C%20any%20hope%20for%20economic%20resurgence%20remains%20futile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESnehasis%20Mukhopadhyay%20is%20a%20data%20science%20enthusiast%20with%20a%20penchant%20for%20drawing%20insights%20from%20political%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708687802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23160306%2Fprasoon-srivastav-vDfkrGeRXRE-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradeshs-economy-down-the-rabbit-hole-and-beyond%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20failure%20to%20redistribute%20land%20and%20dismal%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20has%20made%20UP%20an%20economic%20wasteland.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradeshs-economy-down-the-rabbit-hole-and-beyond%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asylum%20seeker%20boat%20pilot%20locked%20up%20after%20deaths%20of%20four%20migrants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708686180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F70x70%2Fskynews-ibrahima-bah-kent-police_6466691.jpg%3F20240223154717%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fibrahima-bah-asylum-seeker-boat-pilot-locked-up-after-death-of-four-migrants-13078980%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20asylum%20seeker%2C%20who%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20manslaughter%20after%20four%20migrants%20on%20board%20his%20%26quot%3Bnot%20remotely%20seaworthy%26quot%3B%20boat%20drowned%2C%20will%20be%20detained%20for%20nine%20years%20and%20six%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A152%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fibrahima-bah-asylum-seeker-boat-pilot-locked-up-after-death-of-four-migrants-13078980%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fibrahima-bah-asylum-seeker-boat-pilot-locked-up-after-death-of-four-migrants-13078980%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fibrahima-bah-asylum-seeker-boat-pilot-locked-up-after-death-of-four-migrants-13078980%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Removing%20Secularism%20Will%20Sound%20the%20Death%20Knell%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%20Justice%20K.M.%20Joseph%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23153316%2Fimage-1861.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20K.M.%20Joseph%20has%20said%20that%20%E2%80%98secularism%E2%80%99%20is%20indispensable%20in%20a%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20you%20take%20away%20secularism%20from%20the%20preamble%2C%20none%20of%20the%20features%20of%20secularism%20would%20go%20away.%20So%20you%20cannot%20take%20away%20Secularism%20from%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecularism%20is%20absolutely%20indispensable%20in%20a%20democracy.%20If%20secularism%20is%20going%20to%20be%20removed%20by%20any%20government%20from%20the%20Preamble%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20by%20merely%20removing%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98secularism%E2%80%99%2C%20you%20are%20removing%20the%20features%20of%20secularism%E2%80%A6even%20if%20it%20is%20removed%2C%20it%20will%20sound%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20these%20remarks%20while%20delivering%20a%20lecture%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20the%20Kerala%20High%20Court%20Advocates%20Association.%20The%20lecture%20was%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20Concept%20of%20Secularism%20under%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fif-any-govt-removes-secularism-from-preamble-it-will-sound-death-knell-of-democracy-justice-km-joseph-250240%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20calls%20from%20certain%20quarters%20to%20remove%20the%20reference%20to%20%E2%80%98secularism%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecularism%20is%20a%20facet%20of%20equality.%20If%20you%20treat%20all%20religions%20equally%2C%20that%20is%20secularism.%20You%20are%20fair%2C%20you%20do%20not%20bias%20or%20patronise.%20This%20is%20substance%20as%20held%20in%20S.R.%20Bommai%20%5Bjudgment%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20idea%20of%20secularism%20is%20that%20religion%20is%20your%20private%20affair%2C%20keep%20it%20private%E2%80%A6%5Bthe%5D%20State%20must%20maintain%20complete%20neutrality.%20This%20is%20the%20substance%20of%20what%20is%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20these%20batch%20of%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20members%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20agreed%20that%20India%20is%20a%20secular%20country%2C%20they%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20specifically%20mention%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20this%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20agreement%20particularly%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20partition%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20birth%20of%20Pakistan%20choosing%20a%20theocratic%20model%2C%20that%20India%20would%20be%20a%20secular%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnity%20in%20diversity%20does%20not%20mean%20you%20can%20wipe%20out%20diversity.%20It%20cannot%20mean%20you%20will%20achieve%20unity%20by%20wiping%20out%20diversity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20secularism%2C%20it%20is%20the%20bounden%20duty%20of%20the%20State%20to%20protect%20the%20lives%20of%20all%20its%20citizens%20regardless%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20caste%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20functionary%2C%20no%20representative%2C%20no%20minister%20can%20endorse%20any%20religion%2C%20can%20take%20sides%20in%20a%20fight%20between%20religions.%20That%20leads%20to%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20other%20religions%20are%20secondary%2C%20which%20is%20not%20because%20all%20religions%20under%20the%20principle%20of%20secularism%20must%20be%20treated%20equally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWdxxlOP4IpA%3Fsi%3D6zxFoKgRj-jfn2OV%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20that%20citizens%20must%20rise%20to%20protect%20secularism%20and%20constitutional%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20point%20in%20lying%20in%20bed%20saying%20I%20will%20not%20protest%20or%20do%20anything%2C%20let%20the%20State%20do%20whatever%20it%20wants.%20You%20mount%20all%20sorts%20of%20criticism%20and%20display%20complete%20impotence%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20your%20own%20actions.%20What%20is%20it%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20contributing%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20he%20mentioned%20the%20fundamental%20duties%20of%20the%20citizens%20enshrined%20under%20Article%2051A%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20particularly%20the%20need%20to%20cultivate%20a%20scientific%20temper%20and%20feeling%20of%20fraternity%20rising%20above%20religions%20and%20other%20divisions%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressed%20hope%20that%20secularism%20will%20survive%20in%20India%2C%20Justice%20Joseph%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20still%20optimistic%20that%20secularism%20will%20survive.%20My%20optimism%20comes%20largely%20from%20the%20catholicity%20of%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20itself.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20Hindus%20are%20completely%20broadminded%20and%20tolerant%20and%20they%20do%20not%20treat%20religion%20in%20the%20manner%20religion%20is%20treated%20in%20other%20religions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20shores%20of%20this%20country%20were%20opened%20to%20other%20religions%2C%20including%20Christianity%20and%20Islam%20when%20there%20was%20no%20war.%20When%20Islam%20came%20in%208th%20century%2C%20they%20came%20as%20traders.%20When%20Christianity%20came%2C%20there%20was%20no%20army%20marching%20by%20their%20side.%20The%20shores%20of%20the%20country%20were%20thrown%20open%20by%20the%20kings%2C%20the%20priests%E2%80%A6Hinduism%20is%20essentially%20based%20on%20the%20quest%20for%20universal%20truth%20at%20the%20highest%20level%E2%80%A6in%20Hinduism%20you%20will%20find%20the%20dualism%20of%20Madhavacharya%2C%20non-dualism%20of%20Shankaracharya%E2%80%A6so%20the%20very%20innate%20faith%20which%20Hinduism%20is%20such%20that%20it%20is%20broadminded%20to%20absorb%20other%20faiths.%20The%20problem%20arises%20when%20it%20is%20abused%2C%20misused%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20politics%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20gaining%20power.%20That%20is%20where%20the%20greatest%20danger%20lies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708686010000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23153316%2Fimage-1861.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fremoving-secularism-will-sound-the-death-knell-of-democracy-former-sc-judge-justice-k-m-joseph%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20idea%20of%20secularism%20is%20that%20religion%20is%20your%20private%20affair%2C%20keep%20it%20private%E2%80%A6%5Bthe%5D%20State%20must%20maintain%20complete%20neutrality%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justice%20Joseph.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fremoving-secularism-will-sound-the-death-knell-of-democracy-former-sc-judge-justice-k-m-joseph%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hezbollah%20says%202%20paramedics%2C%20fighter%20dead%20in%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20Lebanon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708685630000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107943628%2Cimgsize-1600552.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhezbollah-says-2-paramedics-fighter-dead-in-i