.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Feducation%2Fnews%2Fap-inter-1st-2nd-year-hall-tickets-2024-download-admit-card-at-bieapapcfssin%2Farticleshow%2F107919961.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Board%20of%20Intermediate%20Education%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20has%20released%20the%20AP%20Inter%201st%20year%20and%202nd%20year%20hall%20tickets%20for%202024.%20The%20exams%20will%20start%20in%20March%20and%20students%20are%20advised%20to%20download%20and%20carry%20their%20hall%20tickets%20to%20the%20exam%20centre.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22RAVI%20SHANKAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Feducation%2Fnews%2Fap-inter-1st-2nd-year-hall-tickets-2024-download-admit-card-at-bieapapcfssin%2Farticleshow%2F107919961.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Dry%20Rajasthan%2C%20a%20Computer%20Teacher%20Is%20Earning%20Rs%2020%20Lakh%20Per%20Harvest%20From%20Pearl%20Farming%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20short%20spell%20of%20monsoon%20coupled%20with%20scanty%20rainfall%2C%20Rajasthan%20is%20considered%20the%20most%20water-deficient%20state%20in%20the%20country.%20Unhindered%20by%20water%20issues%20of%20the%20dry%20region%2C%20Vinod%20Bharti%20turned%20to%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%2C%20arguably%20the%20most%20lucrative%20aquaculture%20business%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20pearl%20farming%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20potential%20economically%20viable%20opportunity%20at%20a%20time%20when%20he%20had%20lost%20all%20ways%20of%20earning%20a%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%2045%2C000%2C%20the%20former%20teacher%20now%20generates%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20per%20batch%20with%20pearl%20farming.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20established%20a%20market%20base%20not%20only%20in%20India%20but%20also%20internationally%20in%20the%20UAE%20and%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20a%20handful%20of%20farmers%20who%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267186%2Fpearl-farming-cultivation-oyster-shell-home-made-pond-set-up-ashok-manwani-kuljana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoyster%20pearl%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Rajasthan%2C%20this%20move%20earned%20him%20widespread%20recognition%20from%20people%2C%20including%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20and%20Ashok%20Gehlot.%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20learn%20how%20he%20reaped%20huge%20profits%20with%20the%20novel%20farming%20technique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-4-1708610636.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20the%20last%20batch%2C%20Vinod%20managed%20to%20extract%2010%2C000%20pearls.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-4-1708610636.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-4-1708610636-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-4-1708610636-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-4-1708610636-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-4-1708610636-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342940%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20last%20batch%2C%20Vinod%20managed%20to%20extract%2010%2C000%20pearls.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20failure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20g