19%20introduced%20him%20to%20facets%20of%20integrating%20tech%20into%20business%20and%20commercialising%20an%20idea%20for%20social%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Akshay%20was%20selected%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%E2%80%99s%20RKVY-RAFTAAR%20Scheme%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338349%2Fhow-to-grow-saffron-with-aeroponics-online-classes-himachal-pradesh-solan-mushrooms%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20of%20agriculture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20allied%20sectors.%20While%20the%20idea%20of%20biofertilisers%20had%20taken%20root%20in%20his%20mind%2C%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20delved%20into%20the%20manufacturing%20process.%20But%20whilst%20at%20IITBHU%2C%20he%20recalls%20a%20seminar%20that%20helped%20him%20with%20his%20eureka%20moment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20observed%20that%20the%20processes%20of%20developing%20biofuel%20and%20biofertiliser%20were%20very%20similar.%20Both%20involve%20agricultural%20biomass%20being%20treated%20with%20microbes.%E2%80%9D%20Thus%20began%20the%20journey%20of%20Akshay%20and%20his%20mentor%20testing%20different%20kinds%20of%20microbes%20across%20farming%20lands%20for%20their%20characteristics%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20see%20which%20would%20work%20best%20when%20added%20to%20fertilisers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%202020%2C%20Akshay%20had%20managed%20to%20come%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338548%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-earns-huge-profits-by-growing-strawberry-farm-near-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20set%20of%20biofertilisers%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20all%20performing%20well.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20he%20formally%20launched%20LCB%20Fertilizers%20Pvt%20Ltd.%20But%20just%20when%20things%20were%20looking%20up%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20prepared%20microbe%20mixes%20in%20the%20laboratory%20and%20were%20in%20the%20process%20of%20testing%20the%20mixes%20on%20plants%20to%20check%20their%20efficiency.%20I%20had%20to%20return%20home%20with%20no%20idea%20of%20when%20I%20could%20get%20back%20to%20the%20lab.%20In%20the%20time%20that%20I%20was%20away%2C%20the%20microbe%20mixes%20had%20dried%20up%20and%20were%20now%20useless.%20I%20was%20back%20to%20square%20one%20%E2%80%94%20no%20lab%2C%20no%20money%20and%20no%20hope%20for%20what%20is%20next.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisappointment%20at%20having%20been%20so%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338048%2Fterrace-garden-tips-by-hyderabad-woman-grows-organic-vegetables-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclose%20to%20the%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20having%20to%20give%20up%2C%20clouded%20Akshay%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20During%20this%20time%20he%20was%20also%20offered%20a%20job%2C%20but%20a%20gut%20feeling%20told%20him%20he%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20on%20his%20dream%20just%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20next%20day%2C%20with%20a%20Rs%2010%2C000%20investment%2C%20Akshay%20decided%20to%20turn%20his%20shed%20outside%20his%20home%20into%20his%20lab.%20%E2%80%9CI%20purchased%20a%20pump%20from%20Amazon%2C%20a%20temperature%20sensor%20and%20I%20set%20up%20a%20bioreactor%20in%20my%20house.%20I%20had%20the%20know-how%20to%20prepare%20the%20fertiliser.%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20it%20at%20home.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20Akshay%20went%20around%20collecting%20old%20wood%2C%20and%20soil%20from%20different%20types%20of%20environments%20%E2%80%94%20from%20harsh%20climates%2C%20marshy%20areas%20to%20loamy%20soil%20and%20cow%20dung.%20The%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337129%2Feroponics-tower-planter-for-balcony-garden-by-