hebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342777%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai-based%20Raghuveer%20Surupa%2C%20founder%20of%20Stemtech%20Medical%20Devices%2C%20created%20the%20Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%20to%20help%20patients%20experiencing%20hair%20loss%20during%20chemotherapy.%20The%20system%2C%20designed%20to%20protect%20hair%20follicles%2C%20was%20showcased%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20and%20received%20a%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20investment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342777%2Fprevent-hair-loss-chemotherapy-cancer-care-raghuveer-surupa-eva-scalp-cooling-system-shark-tank%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teacher%20Spends%20Rs%203%20Lakh%20Savings%20To%20Transform%20Govt%20School%2C%20Student%20Strength%20Rises%20by%205X!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhat%20propels%20a%20person%20to%20undertake%20something%20they%E2%80%99ve%20never%20done%20before%3F%20To%20embark%20on%20a%20monumental%20task%2C%20armed%20with%20only%20faith%20in%20their%20heart%3F%20According%20to%20Gopal%20Bhalwala%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F123875%2Fgovernment-school-teacher-and-his-puppets-have-a-very-important-message-for-our-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGovernment%20teacher%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Rajgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20it%20takes%20is%20passion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20he%20undertook%20the%20challenge%20of%20transforming%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20dilapidated%20school%20he%20was%20assigned%20to%20teach%20in%202018%2C%20he%20did%20so%20with%20unwavering%20determination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20risk%20of%20sounding%20too%20unrealistic%2C%20I%20want%20to%20emphasise%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20renovating%20the%20school%2C%20I%20had%20nothing%20but%20a%20passion%20towards%20education.%20The%20schoo