d%20on%2028%20August.%20Once%20in%20Dubai%2C%20we%20hit%20the%20road%20and%20reached%20the%20UK%20on%2026%20October.%20In%20total%2C%20the%20journey%20took%20us%2076%20days.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutting%20their%20faith%20in%20the%20most%20feasible%20route%20suggested%20by%20Google%20Maps%2C%20they%20embarked%20on%20their%20trip.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Dubai%20to%20London%20route%20was%20what%20we%20settled%20on%20after%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340909%2Fbest-homestay-in-manali-afsana-homestay-apple-orchards-himachal-pradesh-snowfall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploring%20several%20different%20routes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20ones%20through%20Russia%2C%E2%80%9D%20Daman%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20time%20spent%20in%20the%20two%20and%20a%20half%20months%20driving%20through%2016%20countries%2C%20Daman%20and%20his%20family%20have%20watched%20the%20world%20through%20a%20window%2C%20literally%20and%20metaphorically.%20%E2%80%9CLandscapes%20changed%2C%20time%20zones%20shifted%2C%20we%20watched%20it%20all%20in%20real-time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20gazing%20off%20into%20the%20distance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20that%20he%20is%20mentally%20still%20in%20those%20lands%20he%20speaks%20of%20so%20fondly.%20But%20how%20much%20did%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340559%2Ftravel-tips-for-people-with-disability-to-make-travelling-safe-where-to-book%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emind-boggling%20trip%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20may%20ask%3F%20%E2%80%9CRoughly%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20Mercedes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Daman%20says%20cheekily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAround%20the%20world%20in%2076%20days%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Daman%20never%20saw%20Lal%20Pari%20as%20a%20car.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20would%20