2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Daman%20recounts%20how%20a%20man%20named%20Anil%20helped%20him%20through%20a%20sticky%20spot.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20car%20had%20broken%20down%20and%20it%20was%20very%20expensive%20to%20hire%20a%20pickup%20truck%20there.%20I%20had%20visited%20Anil%20for%20a%20few%20car-related%20things%20the%20previous%20day%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20car%20broke%20down%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20could%20send%20someone%20to%20help.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20Anil%20drive%20600%20miles%20to%20help%20but%20did%20not%20charge%20a%20penny%20for%20it.%20%E2%80%9CYesterday%20when%20you%20drove%20Lal%20Pari%20to%20my%20garage%2C%20you%20brought%20a%20smile%20to%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20face.%20I%20cannot%20charge%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20was%20Anil%E2%80%99s%20excuse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%E2%80%99s%20more%20fascinating%20is%20the%20number%20of%20people%20Daman%20met%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334987%2Fmumbai-battling-rheumatoid-arthritis-parvinder-chawla-shares-tips-on-wheelchair-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20incredible%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20undertook%20%E2%80%93%20fifty%20thousand%20people%20and%20counting!%20And%20when%20he%20finally%20reached%20the%20destination%2C%20the%20exhilaration%20was%20visible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.25-PM-1-1708430582.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lal%20Pari%20encountered%20all%20sorts%20of%20weather%20on%20this%20adventurous%20voyage%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.25-PM-1-1708430582.jpeg%201024w%2C%20h