hatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-7.29.26-PM-6-1708430653-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342441%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20support%20vehicle%20tagged%20behind%20Lal%20Pari%20the%20entire%20journey%20and%20it%20was%20loaded%20with%20all%20the%20luggage%20the%20family%20had%20packed%20for%20the%20trip.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20the%20start%20of%20the%20journey%20was%20equally%20emotional.%20It%20was%20something%20I%E2%80%99d%20been%20dreaming%20of%20for%20the%20longest%20time%20and%20to%20get%20out%20in%20Dubai%20and%20onto%20the%20road%20was%20amazing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20documentation%20process%20and%20obtaining%20a%20%3Cem%3Ecarnet%20de%20passage%3C%2Fem%3E%20(passport%20for%20the%20car%20that%20enables%20it%20to%20travel%20across%20countries)%20that%20they%20learnt%20that%20they%20were%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indians%20to%20undertake%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334177%2Fbest-travel-startups-in-india-local-experiences-tentgram-curtain-call-adventures-not-on-map%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20expedition%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20this%20kind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoing%20the%20trip%20with%20my%20family%20added%20to%20the%20magic%2C%E2%80%9D%20Daman%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20so%20much%20joy%20when%20we%20accomplished%20it%2C%20and%20a%20feeling%20of%20gratitude%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20what%20many%20may%20have%20dreamt%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20the%20magic%20of%20travel%20evokes%20a%20unanimous%20feeling.%20It%20is%20ingrained%20in%20our%20DNA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhether%20it%20was%20Vasco%20da%20Gama%20exploring%20the%20world%2C%20or%20you%20and%20I%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329567%2Fmumbai-homestay-with-organic-farming-food-forest-sustainable-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravel%20is%20intrinsic%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20our%20existence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Today%2C%20Lal%20Pari%20is%20back%20in%20Daman%E2%80%99s%20garage%20in%20their%20Ahmedabad%20home%20after%20the%20long%20and%20telling%20adventure%20she%E2%80%99s%20been%20on.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20my%20imagination%20but%20it%20seems%20like%20Lal%20Pari%20is%20shining%20a%20little%20bit%20brighter%2C%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20exciting%20adventure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photo%20credits%20are%20attributed%20to%20Vinay%20Panjwani)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708436911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftravel-1708429933.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342428%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gujarat's%20Daman%20Thakore%20and%20his%20family%20drove%20their%20classic%201950%20MG%20YT%20on%20a%2013%2C500%20km%20road%20trip%20from%20Ahmedabad%20to%20London%20spanning%2016%20countries.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20their%20lifechanging%20journey%20in%20the%20'Lal%20Pari'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342428%2Fgujarat-daman-thakore-family-drives-vintage-car-from-ahmedabad-to-london-europe-road-trip%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%E2%80%99s%20Smart%20Stove%20Reduces%20Indoor%20Smoke%20by%2070%25%2C%20Saving%20Lives%20in%203%20Million%20Rural%20Homes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELalita%20Marshkole%E2%80%99s%20day%20would%20start%20promptly%20at%204%20am%20each%20morning%20as%20she%20prepared%20breakfast%20for%20her%20family%20of%20four.%20She%20devoted%20hours%20to%20cooking%20on%20the%20traditional%20mud%20%3Cem%3Echulha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(cooking%20stove)%20before%20packing%20lunch%20for%20her%20two%20children%20and%20heading%20off%20to%20work.%20After%20finishing%20work%2C%20she%20faced%20the%20challenging%20task%20of%20gathering%20firewood%20for%20cooking.%20She%20had%20to%20carry%20several%20kilograms%20of%20wood%20on%20her%20head%20as%20she%20made%20her%20way%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-saroj-prajapati-founder-moms-magic-pickle-mango-madhya-pradesh%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eback%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalita%20and%20her%20husband%20are%20both%20daily%20wage%20labourers%20in%20Badjhir%20village%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Seoni%20district%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ECentre%20for%20Science%20and%20Environment%20(CSE)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20nearly%20500%20million%20people%20in%20India%20lack%20access%20to%20clean%20cooking%20solutions.%20The%20report%20highlights%20that%2041%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20%E2%80%94%20including%20individuals%20like%20Lalita%20%E2%80%94%20rely%20on%20biomass%20as%20cooking%20fuel.%20This%20reliance%20contributes%20to%20approximately%20340%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2013%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smoke%20from%20fuel%20burned%20for%20heating%20and%20cooking%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20contributors%20to%20indoor%20air%20pollution%20in%20India.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20estimates%20that%20every%20year%2C%203.2%20million%20people%20die%20prematurely%20from%20illnesses%20attributable%20to%20household%20air%20pollution%20caused%20by%20the%20incomplete%20combustion%20of%20solid%20fuels%20and%20kerosene%20used%20for%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20long-term%20solution%20for%20this%20is%20the%20usage%20of%20LPG%20stoves%2C%20which%20the%20Government%20is%20providing%20through%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%2C%20many%20are%20yet%20to%20adapt%20to%20it%20as%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20refills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ankit%20Mathur%20came%20across%20this%20problem%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20IIM-Ahmedabad%2C%20in%202008%2C%20he%20started%20looking%20for%20a%20solution%20with%20his%20co-founder%20Neha%20Juneja.%20Interested%20in%20the%20sustainability%20space%2C%20they%20were%20working%20on%20renewable%20energy%20projects%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Here%2C%20they%20came%20face%20to%20face%20with%20the%20daily%20challenges%20in%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20saw%20that%20most%20of%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20time%20was%20spent%20either%20cooking%20or%20collecting%20firewood%20to%20cook.%20After%20observing%20the%20amount%20of%20smoke%20emanating%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Echulhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20studying%20its%20detrimental%20effects%20on%20health%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20work%20on%20a%20clean%20cooking%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20of%20research%20across%20various%20states%20and%20several%20prototypes%20later%2C%20they%20built%20the%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20a%20single-burner%2C%20high-efficiency%20cook%20stove%20that%20reduces%20smoke.%20Since%202012%2C%20Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra%20has%20sold%20three%20million%20cookstoves%20and%20wants%20to%20make%20clean%20cooking%20accessible%20to%20every%20part%20of%20rural%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20access%20to%20clean%20energy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-13-1708433713.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20a