dimentary%20devices%20to%20cook.%20They%20were%20burning%20biomass%20to%20make%20their%20food.%20The%20energy%20efficiency%20of%20biomass%20is%20very%20low.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20burn%201%2C000%20kilojoules%2C%20only%20one-tenth%20gets%20transferred%20to%20the%20cookstove%2C%20making%20it%20very%20wasteful%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20they%20resolved%20to%20develop%20an%20enhanced%20and%20environmentally%20friendly%20cookstove%20to%20alleviate%20the%20workload%20of%20women%20in%20rural%20regions.%20Beginning%20in%202010%2C%20Ankit%2C%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%2C%20and%20Neha%2C%20an%20industrial%20engineer%2C%20teamed%20up%20with%20Shoeb%20Kazi%2C%20a%20chemical%20engineer%2C%20to%20design%20an%20energy-efficient%20%E2%80%98smart%E2%80%99%20stove.%20The%20trio%20worked%20on%20building%20a%20prototype%2C%20conducting%20tests%2C%20and%20engaging%20in%20sales%20directly%20within%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20conscious%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ankit%2C%20about%20their%20stoves%20being%20priced%20at%20Rs%20500.%20They%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20much%20people%20were%20willing%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20a%20major%20portion%20of%202010%20and%202011%2C%20they%20journeyed%20through%20over%2030%20villages%20spanning%2010%20districts%20across%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340464%2Fmadhopatti-uttar-pradesh-ias-factory-upsc-ips-irs-pcs-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Over%20this%20time%2C%20they%20constructed%20more%20than%2010%20prototypes%20and%2C%20guided%20by%20consumer%20feedback%2C%20refined%20their%20design%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20winning%20model%2C%20the%20Greenway%20Smart%20Stove.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20unique%20abo