s-easy-tips-thrissur-nymphaea-sree%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Lenovo%20Used%20Technology%20to%20Revive%20the%20Lost%20Millets%20of%20a%20Kerala%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20published%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Lenovo%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kanthalloor%20Grama%20Panchayat%20President%20P%20T%20Mohandas%20was%20campaigning%20for%20elections%20in%202020%2C%20he%20saw%20huge%20sacks%20lying%20in%20several%20households.%20On%20inquiry%2C%20he%20found%20that%20each%20of%20the%20tribal%20households%20there%20had%20almost%20500%20to%201%2C000%20kg%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329588%2Fentrepreneur-startup-green-energy-foundation-gud-mom-millet-products-help-organic-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinger%20millet%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E)%20lying%20unused.%20Reason%20%E2%80%94%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20sell%20it%20and%20used%20this%20superfood%20solely%20for%20self-consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESomething%20had%20to%20be%20done%2C%20thought%20Mohandas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20began%20seeking%20ways%20to%20sell%20the%20surplus%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20uplift%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20livelihoods%2C%20Lenovo%20was%20also%20exploring%20ways%20to%20integrate%20technology%20for%20farmers%E2%80%99%20welfare%20and%20promote%20the%20cultivation%20of%20millets%20in%20Kanthalloor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanthalloor%20was%20once%20home%20to%20over%2018%20varieties%20of%20millet%2C%20according%20to%20farmers.%20But%20over%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20as%20people%20shifted%20towards%20consuming%20more%20rice%20and%20wheat%2C%20millet%20consumption%20gradually%20reduced%20and%20so%20did%20its%20cultivation.%20The%20village%20lost%20its%20diverse%20variety%20of%20millet%20and%20the%20number%