bitious%20sustainability%20targets%20with%20the%20primary%20goal%20to%20responsibly%20conserve%20and%20source%20water%20for%20all%20our%20projects.%20With%20plants%20incorporating%20advanced%20software%20stack%2C%20Hygenco%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20approach%20enables%20efficiently%20consuming%20renewable%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20commitment%20towards%20leveraging%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20Hygenco%20has%20entered%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20long-term%20green%20hydrogen%20purchase%20agreement%20with%20Jindal%20Stainless%20Limited%20(JSL).%20The%20project%20is%20a%20state-of-the-art%20green%20hydrogen%20facility%20located%20at%20JSL%20steel%20plant%20in%20Hisar%20that%20has%20a%20target%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20considerably%20by%20about%202%2C700%20metric%20tonnes%20per%20annum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20plant%20is%20expected%20to%20produce%2075%20tonnes%20per%20annum%20of%20green%20hydrogen%20using%20roof-top%20and%20floating%20solar%20energy%20sources%20installed%20within%20the%20factory%20premises%2C%20contributing%20towards%20reducing%20carbon%20footprint%20and%20building%20a%20sustainable%20eco-system.%20With%20this%2C%20Hygenco%20will%20run%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20commercial%20long%20term%20offtake%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20step%20to%20provide%20customised%20and%20reliable%20green%20hydrogen%20solutions%2C%20Hygenco%20recently%20signed%20a%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20green%20oxygen%20offtake%20agreement%20with%20Sterlite%20Technologies%20Ltd%20(STL)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20global%20optical%20and%20digital%20solutions%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20project%20is%20expected%20to%20supply%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20green%20oxygen%20to%20STL%E2%80%99s%20state-of-the-art%20glass%20preform%20plant%20based%20out%20of%20Aurangabad%2C%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20s